Kwiyongera byihuse kw'ibimenyetso bya coronavirus (COVID-19) mu muryango w'ubumwe bw'uburayi/Akarere k'ubukungu k'uburayi n'ubwongereza kuva tariki ya 1 Mutarama kugeza tariki ya 15 Werurwe 2020.
Umubare w'abandura wa COVID-19 ugenda wiyongera mu bihugu bigize EU/EEA, kandi u Bwongereza bwagaragaje ko nubwo buri gihugu kiri mu byiciro bitandukanye, icyorezo cya COVID-19 gikomeje kwiyongera mu bihugu byose.
Hashingiwe ku byaranze Ubutaliyani, ibihugu, ibitaro n'inzego z'ubuvuzi byagombye kongera imyiteguro yo guhangana n'ubwiyongere bw'abarwayi ba COVID-19 bazagomba kwitabwaho cyane cyane mu buryo bw'ubuvuzi.
Ku ya 31 Ukuboza 2019, icyorezo cya pneumonia, kitaramenyekana icyateye iyi ndwara, cyatangajwe mu mujyi wa Wuhan, mu ntara ya Hubei mu Bushinwa.
Ku ya 9 Mutarama 2020, Ikigo cy'Ubushinwa gishinzwe kugenzura no gukumira indwara cyatangaje ko icyateye iyi virusi ari coronavirus nshya yerekeza kuri coronavirus ya 2 y'icyorezo cy'indwara z'ubuhumekero zikomeye (SARS-CoV-2).
Kuva icyo gihe, indwara iterwa na SARS-CoV-2 yitwa Coronavirus (COVID-19).
Ibimenyetso kugeza ubu ni uko 80% by'abanduye COVID-19 bafite uburwayi bworoheje, ni ukuvuga ubwandu bwo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero bufite cyangwa budafite indwara y'ibihaha, kandi abenshi muri abo barakira.
Mu bipimo 14 ku ijana, COVID-19 yateye imbere mu buryo bukomeye cyane, ikeneye kuruhuka mu bitaro, mu gihe 6% yongeyeho uburwayi bukomeye cyane bukeneye kwitabwaho cyane.
Imibare y'abapfa mu bitaro kubera COVID-19 ni 4%.
Muri ubu bushakashatsi, twasuzumye uko ubwandu bwa COVID-19 bwagiye bwiyongera muri buri gihugu cyo mu muryango w'ubumwe bw'Uburayi/Akarere k'ubukungu bw'Uburayi (EU/EEA) n'Ubwongereza, maze tugereranya n'intara ya Hubei mu Bushinwa.
Twagereranyije kandi imibare y'abarwayi ba COVID-19 muri iki gihe mu bihugu bigize EU/EEA n'u Bwongereza n'umubare w'abarwayi bo mu Butaliyani mu gihe cy'itariki ya 31 Mutarama kugeza ku ya 15 Werurwe 2020.
Abanduye COVID-19 mu bihugu bigize Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi/Akarere ka Afurika y'Iburengerazuba n'u Bwongereza.
Nyuma yo gutera u Bushinwa, COVID-19 yakomeje gukwirakwira, kandi icyorezo cya COVID-19 ku isi muri iki gihe gikomeje gukurikirana inzira y'u Bushinwa.
Ku ya 11 Werurwe 2020, umuyobozi mukuru w'ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) yatangaje ko COVID-19 ari icyorezo cyugarije isi yose.
Mu cyiciro cya 5 cy'ubushakashatsi bwakozwe na Eurosurveillance 2020, Spiteri n'abandi batangaje ko icyorezo cya COVID-19 cyemejwe bwa mbere n'u Burayi, hashingiwe ku mibare y'ubwandu bw'ishami ry'umuryango w'abibumbye ryita ku buzima (OMS).
Mu bihugu by'i Burayi/Akarere ka EEC, abantu batatu bemejwe bwa mbere babonetse mu Bufaransa ku ya 24 Mutarama 2020 bagarutse baturutse mu mujyi wa Wuhan, mu ntara ya Hubei mu Bushinwa.
Kugeza ku ya 15 Werurwe 2020, COVID-19 yari imaze kugaragara mu bihugu 30 bigize EU/EEA n'Ubwongereza, aho kuva ku ya 31 Ukuboza 2019 kugeza kuri uwo munsi, habonetse abantu 39,768 banduye iyi ndwara, naho 1,727 muri bo barapfuye, muri bo 17,750 banduye n'abandi 1,441 bapfuye mu Butaliyani honyine.
Fata imibare yose n'ibyabaye nk'iterambere ry'umubare w'abanduye COVID-19.
Mu kigo cy'u Burayi gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara (ECDC), imibare y'ubwandu bwa COVID-19 bw'igihugu ku isi, itangwa n'ibanze nk'ibiro by'ubuzima, inzego z'ubuzima ku rwego rw'igihugu n'akarere, n'ishami ry'umuryango w'abibumbye ryita ku buzima, iherutse gusubirwamo buri munsi saa munani za mu gitondo.
Aya makuru yose yakoreshejwe mu igenzura ry'icyorezo cya COVID-19 mu bihugu bigize EU/EEA, ndetse no mu Bwongereza, kandi agereranywa n'amakuru yo mu Butaliyani.
Nk'uko bigaragara ku barwayi bakomeje kwibasirwa na COVID-19, twagerageje kubara imibare y'abarwayi ba COVID-19 mu minsi 14, dukurikije uko ubwandu bwa COVID-19 busanzwe bwifashe muri buri gihugu cyo mu muryango w'ubumwe bw'Uburayi/Akarere k'ubukungu bw'Uburayi (EU/EEA) n'Ubwongereza, kuva ku ya 1 Mutarama kugeza ku ya 15 Werurwe 2020.
Nanone kandi, twerekanye umubare wiyongereye w'ubwandu buri gihugu cyatangaje ku itariki ya 15 Werurwe 2020 saa munani z'ijoro, ugereranyije n'uw'u Butaliyani mu gihe cy'itariki ya 31 Mutarama kugeza ku itariki ya 15 Werurwe 2020.
Imibare ya COVID-19 mu bihugu by'u Burayi/Akarere ka Burayi n'u Bwongereza
Imibare y'ubwandu bwa COVID-19 mu gihe cy'iminsi 14 mu bihugu bigize EU/EEA n'Ubwongereza, ikurikiza imibare y'ubwandu bw'ubwandu bwo mu ntara ya Hubei (Ubushinwa) (Igishushanyo cya 1).
Ku muryango w'ubumwe bw'Uburayi/Umuryango w'ubukungu w'Uburayi n'u Bwongereza muri rusange, ubwandu bwa COVID-19 bwatangiye kwiyongera ku itariki ya 21 Gashyantare, nyuma buza kwiyongera cyane ku itariki ya 28 Gashyantare 2020.
Ibi ahanini byatewe n'ubwiyongere bwihuse bw'imibare y'abandura yavuzwe n'u Butaliyani, ariko ibihugu by'u Burayi/Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi n'u Bwongereza byerekanye ukwiyongera guhambaye kw'ibimenyetso by'ubwiyongere bwa COVID-19.
Igishushanyo cya 2 kigaragaza umubare munini w'abanduye COVID-19 mu bihugu by'Uburayi/Akarere k'Ubukungu k'Uburayi (EU/EEA) n'Ubwongereza ugereranyije n'u Butaliyani mu gihe cy'itariki ya 31 Mutarama kugeza ku ya 15 Werurwe 2020.
Raporo igaragaza ko ku itariki ya 15 Werurwe saa munani z'igitondo, ibindi bihugu 15 byo mu muryango w'ubumwe bw'Uburayi/Akarere k'ubukungu bw'Uburayi n'Ubwongereza, byatangaje umubare muto w'abanduye, ugereranyije n'uw'abanduye mu Butaliyani, mu byumweru bitatu gusa cyangwa se mu gihe gito.
Ibyavuye mu bushakashatsi bwacu byerekanye ko umubare w'abanduye COVID-19 wazamutse cyane mu bihugu bigize EU/EEA n'u Bwongereza.
Kuba ibintu byagiye bihinduka mu buryo butunguranye mu cyorezo cya COVID-19 bigaragaza ko iki cyorezo kigenda gihinduka ku muvuduko ungana mu bihugu byose.
Ibi ni ukubera ko ibihugu biri mu byiciro bitandukanye, impinduka mu bisubizo by'ubuzima rusange bw'igihugu n'ibisobanuro by'ubwandu mu bihugu bitandukanye, n'ibirori bitandukanye byo guhitamo abarwayi bagomba gupimwa kugira ngo bamenye COVID-19, harimo no gupima.
Mu ntangiriro za Werurwe 2020, abaganga bo mu bice by'u Butaliyani byazahajwe cyane batangaje ko 10% by'abarwayi ba COVID-19 bakeneye kwitabwaho cyane, kandi amakuru atandukanye avuga ko ibitaro ndetse n'urwego rw'ubuvuzi bukomeye muri utwo turere byakoze ibishoboka byose.
Amakuru ajyanye no kwakira COVID-19 mu bitaro na/cyangwa mu bigo byita ku barwayi bakomeye ubu araboneka ku rwego rw'Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'Uburayi/Akarere ka Burayi ku kigero cya 6% na 1% by'abanduye gusa (amakuru ntabwo agaragara).
Ariko kandi, bigomba gukusanywa mu buryo bwa sisitemu kugira ngo byuzuze amakuru y'ubugenzuzi arebana n'umubare w'abamaze kwandura n'umubare w'abapfuye.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mu 2010-11 bwagaragaje itandukaniro rinini ry'ubuvuzi bw'ibanze n'ibitanda by'ubwitonzi mu Burayi, kuva kuri 29.2 mu Budage kugeza kuri 4.2 ku baturage 100,000 muri Porutugali.
Ibi bivuze ko ibihugu bishobora kugira umutungo munini cyangwa muke ugereranyije n'u Butaliyani (aho hari imyanya 12.5 yo kwita ku barwayi n'ibitanda byo kwita ku barwayi ku baturage 100,000 mu 2010-11).
Imiterere y'icyitegererezo yerekeranye no kubura ubushobozi mu by'ubuvuzi yatanzwe mu igenzura rishya ry'ibyago bya COVID-19 rya ECDC, rigereranya ibihugu bigize EU/EEA n'Ubwongereza ko abarwayi ba COVID-19 bafite ibyago byo kurenza ubushobozi bwo kwita ku barwayi bakomeye &gt; 90%.
Kubera ko abenshi mu barwayi bakunze kugaragara mu bice bimwe by'ibihugu by'i Burayi, mu karere k'ubukungu k'i Burayi n'u Bwongereza, kandi ibitaro n'inzego z'ubuvuzi bikunze gukorera abaturage bo mu karere runaka gusa, amakuru y'abarwayi n'ubuvuzi bw'ubuvuzi bigomba gutangwa ku izina ry'inzego z'ibanze z'ubwiru bwa kabiri (NUTS-2).
Ubunararibonye bwo mu Butaliyani n'ubushakashatsi buri gukorwa mu bindi bihugu byerekana ko icyorezo cya COVID-19 ku isi kigenda gihinduka mu bihugu bigize Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi/Umuryango w'Ubukungu bw'u Burayi (EU/EEA) n'Ubwongereza.
Ibihugu, ibitaro n'inzego z'ubuvuzi rero bigomba kwitondera gutegura uko bizagenda mu gihe hazabaho uburyo bushya bwo kwanduza SARS-CoV-2 mu baturage, hashobora kuba hari ubwandu bw'icyorezo n'ubwiyongere bw'abarwayi ba COVID-19 bakeneye kwitabwaho cyane cyane mu buryo bw'ubuvuzi, nk'uko bimeze ku kibazo kiri kuba mu bice byugarijwe n'iki cyorezo mu Butaliyani.
Nk'uko byagaragajwe mu isuzuma ry'ibyago rishya ryakozwe na ECDC, uburyo bwihuse, buhuje n'igihe kandi bufite ireme, ni ngombwa mu gutinza ikwirakwira rya SARS-COV-2, uhereye ku guhangana n'ubwandu ugana ku buryo bwo kugabanya, mu gihe ukwiyongera k'umubare w'abandura bishobora kudahesha abafata ibyemezo n'ibitaro igihe gihagije cyo kumenya no kwakira no gusubiza mu buryo bukwiriye mu gihe bidashyizweho mu bikorwa hakiri kare.
Gushyira mu gaciro ibyago byihuse na byo byashyizeho ingamba z'ubuzima rusange zo kugabanya ingaruka z'icyorezo.
Hari umwanya muto mu gihe ibihugu bishobora kongera imbaraga mu bikorwa by'ubuyobozi mu kugabanya ikwirakwira rya SARS-CoV-2 no kugabanya igitutu ku nzego z'ubuzima.
Iyo bitoye, sisitemu z'ubuzima mu bihugu by'Uburayi / mu bindi bihugu by'ubukungu bw'Uburayi zishobora guhura n'ubwiyongere bw'abarwayi bakeneye kwitabwaho cyane mu minsi cyangwa ibyumweru biri imbere.
Icyorezo cya Coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19), cyatewe n'indwara y'ubuhumekero ikaze (SARS) iterwa na Coronavirus 2 (SARS-CoV-2), kugeza ubu kimaze kwica abantu barenga 3,000 no kwandura abarenga 80,000 mu Bushinwa no mu bindi bice by'isi, bituma abantu bahura n'akaga.
Iyi virusi ifitanye isano na virusi ifite umwihariko umwe, SARS-CoV, yatumye abantu babarirwa mu bihumbi barwara SARS mu 2003. SARS-CoV-2 ishobora kwandura mu bihaha kandi igatera ibimenyetso bisa nk'iby'iyi virusi ya SARS-CoV.
Nyamara COVID-19 ifite ubukana buciriritse n'ubwandu buciriritse kurusha SARS, ariko ni indwara yandura cyane kandi yibasira abantu bakuze kurusha urubyiruko, kandi igera ku bagabo kurusha abagore.
Mu gusubiza umubare ugenda wiyongera w'ibitabo ku ndwara zikwirakwira, iyi ngingo ishaka gutanga isesengura rihuje n'igihe kandi rirambuye ku ngingo z'ubushakashatsi zihindagurika mu buryo bwihuse.
Tuzaganira ku byiciro by'ibanze by'indwara, impamvu ziterwa n'indwara, uburyo bwo kuzishyira mu kato, kuzirwanya no kuzirinda.
Nubwo hari ibibazo byinshi bitarabonerwa ibisubizo, twizeye ko ubu bushakashatsi buzasobanura neza kandi bugatuma dushobora kurwanya iyi ndwara iteye ubwoba.
Umunsi mukuru wa Noheli wo ku ya 25 Mutarama 2020 wabaye udasanzwe kandi utazibagirana ku Bashinwa bose basabwe kuguma mu ngo zabo mu biruhuko no mu byumweru byakurikiye icyorezo cya virusi nshya.
Iyi virusi ifite imiterere isa n'iya coronavirus (CoV) yatumye habaho icyorezo cy'indwara ifata imyakura (SARS) mu 2003. Ni yo mpamvu yashyizwe ku rutonde rwa SARS-CoV-2 n'ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) ku wa 11 Gashyantare 2020, naho indi ndwara ifitanye isano na yo yitwa CoV Disease-19 (COVID-19).
Iki cyorezo cyatangiriye i Wuhan mu Bushinwa, gikwira mu gihugu hose ndetse kigakwira mu bihugu bigera kuri 50 ku isi.
Kugeza ku ya 2 Werurwe 2020, virusi yatumye habaho ubwandu bwa COVID-19 bugera ku 80000, aho abarwayi barenga 40,000 barekuwe, abarwayi barenga 3000 barapfuye.
Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima ryavuze ko COVID-19 ari "umwanzi wa mbere w'abaturage" kandi ko ishobora kuba ikomeye kurusha iterabwoba.
Nk'uko PubMed (https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/) ibivuga, mu gihe kitarenze amezi abiri, ubushakashatsi burenga 200 bwamaze gutangwa ku cyorezo cya COVID-19, harimo ubushakashatsi ku ndwara, impamvu, icyorezo n'ubuvuzi kuva hatangajwe bwa mbere ku itariki ya 7 Mutarama 2020, bugaragaza ko virusi ya Covid-19 itandukanye n'izindi ndwara z'ubwandu.
Iyi nyigo igerageza guhuza iterambere ry'ubushakashatsi mu byiciro bishya bihinduka vuba.
Aho bishoboka, tugerageza kugereranya COVID-19 na SARS, ubundi burwayi buterwa na coronavirus (CoV), ari bwo Middle East Respiratory Syndrome (MERS, yavutse mu mwaka wa 2012).
Tuzasuzuma kandi ibyo twize ku bijyanye no kwirinda no guhanura indwara, hamwe n'ibibazo byihutirwa tugomba gusubiza.
Ubusanzwe, virusi za CoV zitwa indwara ziterwa n'ubwandu zidakomeretsa abantu, nyinshi muri zo zikaba ziterwa n'indwara y'ibicurane, zigera kuri 15% by'indwara ya grippe 4.
Nyamara muri iki kinyejana, twabonye virusi za corona (CoVs) zikwirakwiza mu bantu zikubye kabiri, SARS-CoV na MERS-CoV, zatumye habaho icyorezo cya mbere mu Bushinwa mu 2003 no muri Arabiya Sawudite mu 2012, hanyuma zikwirakwira mu bindi bihugu byinshi mu buryo bukabije kandi bufite ubukana.
Ni yo mpamvu COVID-19 ubu ari icyorezo cya gatatu cya coronavirus (CoV) mu mateka y'abantu.
Nk'uko bigaragazwa ku ishusho ya 1.1, icyorezo cy'indwara y'ibicurane by'ubwoko butamenyekana cyatangajwe bwa mbere ku wa 31 Ukuboza 2019 kivuye i Wuhan kiza mu biro bya Komisiyo y'Igihugu y'Ubuzima mu Bushinwa.
Hashize iminsi irindwi, ibipimo by'ubwoko bwa coronavirus (CoV) byasohotse.
Ku ya 15 Mutarama 2020, habonetse umuntu wa mbere wapfuye avuye i Wuhan.
Hagati aho, icyorezo cyakwirakwiriye mu mijyi, intara n'ibihugu by'ibituranyi.
