Ariko kandi, uburwayi n'uburwayi bwo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero ni ibintu bikomeye bibangamira abarwayi, kandi ni na byo bituma abantu bapfa.
Bityo rero, ubufasha bwo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero ni ingenzi mu kugabanya ibimenyetso no kurokora ubuzima, kandi bukubiyemo imiti isanzwe ya ogisijeni, ogisijeni ifite umuvuduko mwinshi, umwuka utinjira utanyura mu mwuka, n'umuyaga w'imashini utuma habaho guhungabana bitewe n'uburemere bw'uburwayi.
Abarwayi bafite ibimenyetso by'ubuhumekero bikomeye bagomba kuvurwa hakoreshejwe umuti witwa extracorporeal membrane oxygenation (ECMO), uburyo bwo kuvura imitsi y'umutima n'amahaha, bukoreshwa mu kuvura indwara z'umutima n'ubuhumekero zangiza ubuzima.
Byongeye kandi, kubungabunga igipimo cya elegitoronike, kwirinda no kuvura nyuma yo kwandura, guhangana n'indwara no kurinda imikorere y'ingingo z'ingenzi, byose ni ngombwa ku barwayi ba SARS-CoV-2.
Birazwi ko ibicurane byo mu Bushinwa biterwa n'uburyo umubiri w'umuntu ugira ubwirinzi bukabije ku barwayi ba SARS na MERS.
Cytokine ni uburyo bwo gusubiza mu buryo bw'ubwirinzi bufite imiterere, bugaragazwa no guturika kwa cytokine zikurikira, harimo TNFα, IL-1β, IL-2, IL-6, IFNα, IFNβ, IFNγ, na MCP-1.
Izi cytokine zituma ingirabuzimafatizo z'umubiri zisohora ibinyabuzima byinshi by'umudendezo, ari byo bitera ARDS n'izindi ndwara ziterwa n'imikorere mibi y'umubiri.
Gukumira indwara ni ngombwa mu kuvura cytocin cyclone, cyane cyane mu barwayi bafite ikibazo gikomeye.
Imiti yitwa Corticosteroids na tocilizumab, ikoreshwa mu kuvura cyorezo cya cytochrome P.
Ubundi buvuzi bw'imiti ya cytocin harimo guhuza ibisubizo by'ubwirinzi by'ingirabuzimafatizo za T, kubuza IFN-γ, IL-1, na TNF, kubuza JAK, gukoresha imiti ya blinatumomab, kubuza cytocin-expressing signaling 4 no kubuza HDAC.
Steroids, umuti ufasha kurwanya indwara z'uburwayi, zakoreshejwe cyane mu kuvura SARS mu kugabanya uburwayi bw'ibicurane by'uburwayi.
Ariko, imiti ya Steroids mu rugero rwo hejuru ntabwo ifite akamaro mu kuvura indwara z'ibihaha zikomeye za SARS na COVID-19.
Ahubwo bishobora guteza ingaruka zikomeye cyane cyane indwara z'umugongo, zigira ingaruka ku cyorezo.
Icyakora, igihe gito cyo gukoresha kortikosteroide mu buryo bworoheje ariko buciriritse, cyasabwaga ko ikoreshwa mu buryo bw'ubwitonzi cyane ku barwayi ba COVID-19 bafite uburwayi bukomeye.
Mu gihe cy'iyi nyandiko, nta muti wa virusi wagaragaye ko ugira ingaruka nziza.
Icyakora, byaje kugaragara ko umuti wa Remdesivir, uterwa mu maraso, wari ufite ingufu mu murwayi w'umunyamerika wa COVID-19.
Remdesivir ni umuti mushya wa antiviral watangijwe na Gilead Biopharmaceuticals mu kuvura indwara ziterwa na Ebola na Marlburg.
Nyuma, umuti wa remdesivir wagaragaje ubushobozi bwo gukumira virusi ziterwa na RNA, harimo MERS na SARS.
Ishingiye kuri ibi byose, Gilead yahaye Ubushinwa ubushobozi bwo gukora ibizamini bibiri ku bantu banduye SARS-CoV-2, kandi ibisubizo byategerejwe cyane.
Byongeye kandi, baricitinb, interferon-α, lopinavir/ritonavir na ribavirin byashyizwe ahagaragara nk'imiti ishobora gukoreshwa mu barwayi bafite ibimenyetso by'ubuhumekero bidasobanutse.
Igituntu, guhohotera, guhohotera, gusenya ingirabuzimafatizo z'igifu n'ibindi bishobora kubaho nyuma yo gufata lopinavir/ritonavir.
Imikorere y'izi miti n'izindi nkingo zikoreshwa mu barwayi igomba kugenzurwa neza.
Plasma yahawe umurwayi wakize n'imikorere y'umubiri
Gukura amaraso mu barwayi bakize indwara zandura, kugira ngo bavurwe n'abandi barwayi bafite iyo ndwara cyangwa se kugira ngo barinde umuntu ufite ubuzima bwiza kurwara iyo ndwara, bimaze igihe kirekire.
Mu by'ukuri, abarwayi bakize baba bafite ingufu nyinshi z'umubiri urwanya indwara mu maraso yabo.
Imibiri ni immunoglobulin (ig) ikorwa na B lymphocytes mu kurwanya indwara, kimwe n'ibindi bintu bidasanzwe bitagaragara mu mubiri, kandi ishobora kumenya molekile ituma indwara ibaho, maze ikajya iyicira.
Ku bw'ibyo, plasma yakusanyijwe mu maraso y'abarwayi bakize COVID-19 izashyirwamo abarwayi 10 barembye.
Ibimenyetso byabo byagiye bihinduka mu masaha 24 binyuze mu kugabanya ubukana bw'ubwandu n'ubw'agakoko gatera virusi, no kongera umwuka wa ogisijeni mu maraso.
Ariko kandi, gukora ubushakashatsi no kwemeza ni ngombwa kugira ngo umuntu agire uburyo bwo gukoresha uburyo bwinshi mbere y'uko haboneka umuti runaka.
Byongeye kandi, kubera imbaraga zo kuvura, hari ibintu bimwe na bimwe bifitanye isano na plazma bigomba kwitabwaho cyane.
Urugero, imiterere y'umubiri ishobora gutuma umubiri udashobora gukora neza cyangwa se ukagira imbaraga zo kurwanya indwara, kandi igatuma habaho ibimenyetso by'uko habaho ikwirakwira ry'imiti ishobora kwica.
Ubusanzwe, ibice by'ingenzi by'umwimerere mu maraso biba ari bike cyane, kandi hakenerwa plasma nyinshi mu kuvura abarwayi bafite ibibazo bikomeye.
Biragoye gukora no gukora imikorere yihariye vuba bihagije kugirango kurwanya ikwirakwira ry'iki cyorezo ku isi hose.
Ni ngombwa kandi birashoboka cyane gutandukanya utwo tugingo tw'ubwoko bwa B mu barwayi bakize no kumenya ubwoko bw'imiterere y'umubiri cyangwa kureba utwo tugingo tw'umubiri dukora neza ku poroteyine y'ingenzi ya virusi.
Ibi bituma dushobora kongera umusaruro w'ibinyabuzima vuba cyane.
TCM imaze imyaka ibarirwa mu bihumbi ikoreshwa mu kuvura indwara zitandukanye mu Bushinwa.
Nyamara, ingaruka zayo ahanini zishingiye ku guhuza ibice byinshi by'ingingo mu buryo bumwe, buhindagurika bitewe n'igaragaza indwara ishingiye ku bitekerezo bya TCM.
Ibyinshi mu bice by'ingenzi bigize ibyo bikoresho biracyari ibisanzwe cyangwa ntibiramenyekana neza kuko bigoye kubikura no kubishyira mu bubiko cyangwa kubikura neza.
Muri iki gihe, kubera kubura ubuvuzi bwikora kandi bwihariye bwa COVID-19, TCM yabaye uburyo bwingenzi bwo kuvura ubundi bufasha ku barwayi bafite ibimenyetso byoroheje cyangwa bito cyangwa abavuwe mu bihe bikomeye.
Urugero, imiti ya Zofengidu na Hwangjin-wen yabonetse ko ifite akamaro mu kuvura COVID-19.
Ibitekerezo by'uko abantu bakira neza mu gihe bavurwa COVID-19 byerekanwa mu ntara zimwe zo mu Bushinwa, aho 87% by'abarwayi bakira TCM, ni ukuvuga abavuye mu ntara ya Guangzhou (63.7%), Ningxi (50%) na Hunan (50%), naho mu ntara ya Hubei, aho abagera kuri 30% bakira TCM, hagaragaye ko umubare w'abarwayi bakira neza ari hasi cyane (13%).
Ariko kandi, iyi ni igereranya ry'uburyo bwo kwihutisha, kubera ko hari ibindi bintu byinshi, urugero nk'umubare n'uburemere bw'abarwayi, bigomba gushyirwa mu igenzura.
Ku ya 18 Gashyantare 2020, Bolichang na bagenzi be basohoye ubushakashatsi bugereranya uburyo bwo kuvura bw'Uburayi bw'Iburengerazuba (WM) bwonyine n'uburyo bwo kuvura bw'ubumwe hagati ya WM na TCM.
Basanze igihe cyasabwaga kugira ngo ubushyuhe bw'umubiri bujye mu buryo, ibimenyetso bigahita bigabanuka, no kuba mu bitaro ku itsinda rya WM+TCM, cyari gito ugereranyije n'itsinda rya WM.
Igishishikaje cyane, ni uko igipimo cy'uburwayi bugenda burushaho kuba bubi (kuva ku rugero ruto kugeza ku rugero rukomeye) cyari gito cyane ku itsinda rya WM + TCM kurusha itsinda rya WM (7.4% kuri 46.2%), kandi igipimo cy'urupfu ruto ku itsinda rya WM + TCM cyari gito cyane kurusha itsinda rya WM (8.8% kuri 39%).
Icyakora, ingaruka n'umutekano wa TCM biracyategereje igerageza ry'ubuvuzi ryakozwe neza ku rwego runini no mu bigo byinshi.
Birashimishije kandi kumenya imikorere y'ibikorwa no kugaragaza uburyo uburyo bwo kuvura TCM cyangwa uburyo bwo kuvura buhuje na bwo, niba bishoboka.
Abarwayi bakekwaho cyangwa bagaragaweho COVID-19 akenshi baba bafite ubwoba bwinshi bw'icyorezo kandi bishobora no gushyira ubuzima bwabo mu kaga, kandi abantu bari mu kato bashobora kugira ubwoba, kwigunga no kurakara.
Byongeye kandi, ibimenyetso by'ubwandu nk'ubushyuhe, guhumeka cyane n'igisebe, kimwe n'ingaruka mbi z'ubuvuzi nko kubura ibitotsi biterwa na korticosteroids, bishobora gutuma umuntu agira imihangayiko myinshi n'imihangayiko.
Mu cyiciro cya mbere cy'icyorezo cya SARS, ibibazo by'uburwayi bwo mu mutwe by'inyongera, urugero nk'agahinda, guhangayika, gutinya, guhangayika, kwibagirwa, no kwiyahura byavuzwe.
Gukurikirana no kwigenzura by'ibanze, bikaba ari bimwe mu bigize igisubizo cy'ubuzima rusange ku cyorezo cya COVID-19, bishobora gutuma abantu bamwe na bamwe batamenya neza kandi bakagira amakenga ku ngaruka z'ubwandu, bigatuma bagenzura no kwigenzura ku miryango yabo n'inshuti zabo.
Ku bw'ibyo, kwita ku buzima bwo mu mutwe bigomba gutangwa ku barwayi ba COVID-19, ku bantu bakekwaho uburwayi, ku bantu bahuye na bo, ndetse no ku baturage muri rusange bakeneye kwitabwaho.
Ubufasha bw'imitekerereze bugomba kuba bukubiyemo gushyiraho amatsinda y'ubushakashatsi mu by'ubuzima bwo mu mutwe, itumanaho risobanutse neza, amakuru ahoraho kandi ahuje n'igihe ku bijyanye n'uburyo bwo kuvura no gutangiza icyorezo cya SARS-CoV-2, no gukoresha ibikoresho bya elegitoroniki n'ibikoresho by'ikoranabuhanga kugira ngo wirinde gushyikirana cyane cyangwa cyane.
Inkingo z'ingirakamaro ni ingenzi mu gukumira ikwirakwira ry'ubwandu bw'inyamaswa n'abantu ku mikorobe ishobora kwandura, kandi akenshi zikoreshwa mu kongerera umuti wa virusi mu kurwanya indwara ziterwa n'ubwandu bushya bukunze kugaragara.
Hari hashyizweho imihati yo gukora urukingo rw'uruhu rwa S kugira ngo ruzatume umubiri n'ubwirinzi bw'umubiri bikomera kandi bikomere mu gihe kirekire, birwanya SARS-CoV.
Urukingo ruzima rwasuzumwe mu ngero z'amatungo ku cyorezo cya SARS.
Icyakora, ubushobozi bw'inkingo z'ubuzima zigeragezwa ku bantu bakuze n'ibimera by'ibanze, n'uko zibakingira virusi ya Zika (gukura mu bantu ukajya mu nyamaswa) bigomba kwemezwa mbere y'uko hakorwa ubushakashatsi bw'ibanze.
Ibi bishobora kuba biterwa n'uko SARS yongeye kugaruka mu myaka 17 ishize, kandi nta muntu mushya wongeye kwandura.
Ahubwo, ubwandu bw'icyorezo cya MERS bukomeje kwiyongera mu Burasirazuba bwo Hagati no mu bindi bice by'isi, bitewe n'uko hatakomeje kubaho ubwandu bw'imiterere ya zoonotic (imiterere y'inyamaswa igera ku bantu) mu turere twanduye.
Imiti yo kurwanya MERS yashyizweho mu buryo bw'ikoranabuhanga ikoreshwa na virusi idakora, ADN plasmides, virusi, nanoparticles, mikorobe nk'iyo, na poroteyine zongeye kuvugururwa, kandi hari n'indi mikorobe yashyizwe mu ngero z'inyamaswa.
Iterambere ry'urukingo rukora neza kandi rukomeye rwa SARS-CoV-2 ku bantu badafite ubwirinzi ni inshingano yihutirwa kandi y'ingenzi mu gukumira icyorezo.
Icyakora, gukomeza gutsinda icyo kibazo kirakomeye kubera ko igihe kirekire (cy'amezi 18 muri rusange) ari cyo gikenewe mu gukora inkingo no guhindura vuba ubwoko butandukanye bwa CoV.
Kubera ko ari ubwoko bushya bwa COVID-19, butangiye kugaragara mu byiciro by'igerageza, mu gihe abarwayi bari ibihumbi.
Mu bihe byinshi, umurwayi ashobora gukira burundu nta kibazo na kimwe.
Nubwo bimeze bityo, COVID-19, isa na SARS na MERS, ifitanye isano n'uburwayi n'urupfu by'abarwayi bafite ibibazo bikomeye.
Kubaka uburyo bwo guhanura indwara ni ngombwa ku bigo by'ubuzima kugira ngo bishyire imbere serivisi zabo, cyane cyane mu turere dufite amikoro make.
Dushingiye ku bushakashatsi bwakozwe mu buryo bw'ibanze bwagaragaye mu gihe cyashize, bimwe mu bintu bikurikira bishobora kugira ingaruka cyangwa bigaterwa n'uko umurwayi wa COVID-19 amerewe (Imbonerahamwe (Imbonerahamwe 33)):
Imyaka: Imyaka ni kimwe mu bintu by'ingenzi byerekana ko SARS na COVID-19 ishobora kubaho.
COVID-19 yibasira cyane cyane abantu bafite imyaka 30-65, aho 47.7% by'abarwayi bari hejuru y'imyaka 50 mu bushakashatsi bwakozwe ku bantu 8,866, nk'uko byavuzwe haruguru.
Abarwayi bakeneye kwitabwaho cyane baba bafite ibyago byo kugira uburwayi budafite ibibazo kandi bafite imyaka myinshi kurusha abatabufite (imyaka 66 kuri 51 ku kigereranyo), ibyo bikaba bigaragaza ko imyaka ari yo ituma habaho uburwayi bwa COVID-19.
Igitsina: SARS-CoV-2 yandura cyane abagabo kurusha abagore (0.31/100,000 kuri 0.27/100,000), nk'uko byavuzwe haruguru.
Guhungabana no gucibwa intege: Abarwayi ba COVID-19 bakeneye kwitabwaho cyane bashobora kugira ububabare buturuka ku guhagarara kw'umutima no kugira umutima udakora neza.
Ibibazo by'umutima biracyari impamvu y'ibanze y'urupfu rw'abarwayi ba SARS.
Hari amakuru avuga ko SARS-CoV-2 ishobora kwinjira mu bice by'ubuhumekero bifite ACE2 bigatuma imikorere y'ibihaha by'abarwayi ba COVID-19 idakora neza.
Birakwiriye kandi ko tumenya ko imyaka n'indwara ziterwa n'uburwayi, bifitanye isano rikomeye cyane, ku buryo bishobora kugira ingaruka ku muntu ku wundi.
Ibyavumbuwe mu malaborative bidasanzwe: Ibipimo bya poroteyine igira uruhare mu gutera C (CRP) mu maraso bigaragaza uburemere bw'igisebe cyangwa icyangiritse, kandi byashyizweho nk'ibimenyetso by'indwara ishobora kuvuka, ibisubizo ku buvuzi n'ubuvuzi bwa nyuma.
Ubufatanye bw'urwego rwa CRP ku buremere n'ibimenyetso bya COVID-19 nabyo byaravuzwe.
Byongeye kandi, kongera lactate dehydrogenase (LDH), aspartate aminotransferase (AST), aminotransferase (ALT) na creatine kinase (CK) nabyo bishobora gufasha mu guhanura ibisubizo.
Iyi enzymes igaragara cyane mu ngingo nyinshi, cyane cyane umutima n'impyiko, kandi irarekurwa mu gihe cy'imikorere mibi y'uruhu.
Ni yo mpamvu ari ibimenyetso bikunze kugaragara ku mutima cyangwa impyiko.
Ibimenyetso by'ibanze by'ibizamini by'ubuvuzi: Gufata amashusho y'igituza no guhindura ibimenyetso mu gihe cy'ibizamini by'ubuvuzi bigomba gufatwa hamwe n'ibindi bibazo by'ibanze mu guhanura ingaruka n'ingaruka za COVID-19.
Gukoresha Steroids: Nkuko byavuzwe haruguru, Steroids ni imiti yo kugabanya ubukana bw'ubwirinzi bw'umubiri ikoreshwa mu kuvura imiti ihuriweho n'indwara zimwe na zimwe z'ibyorezo mu rwego rwo kugabanya ubukana bw'ubwugarizi.
Gukoresha imiti ya korticosteroid mu rugero rwo hejuru ni byo bikoreshwa mu kuvura abarwayi ba SARS ikomeye. Abarokotse bagerwaho n'imihungabana y'amaraso n'amagufa, ituma babaho igihe cyose cyangwa ikagabanya ubuzima bwabo.
Bityo rero, niba ari ngombwa, steroid yagombye gukoreshwa mu rugero ruciriritse kandi mu gihe gito ku barwayi ba COVID-19.
Ihangane: Nk'uko byavuzwe haruguru mu gihe cy'icyorezo cya COVID-19, abarwayi benshi bagize imihangayiko idasanzwe kuko bihanganira igihe kirekire kandi bihangana, gukabya guhangayika, no kubona urupfu rw'abagize umuryango wabo ba bugufi n'abandi barwayi.
Ni ngombwa gutanga inama z'imitekerereze n'ubufasha burambye kugira ngo aba barwayi bashobore kureka imihangayiko no gusubira mu buzima busanzwe.
Dukurikije ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mu bihe byashize, COVID-19 igaragara ko itandukanye cyane na SARS.
Usibye kwanduza mu muyoboro w'ubuhumekero wo hasi, SARS-CoV-2 ishobora kwanduza mu muyoboro w'ubuhumekero wo hejuru kandi igatera ibimenyetso cyangwa nta bimenyetso mu cyiciro cya mbere cy'ubwandu, bikaba bisa n'ibindi birwara bya koronavirusi bitera ibicurane bisanzwe.
Ku bw'ibyo, abarwayi banduye mu gihe cy'icyiciro cya mbere cyangwa mbere yo kugaragaza ibimenyetso bashobora gukora ingano nini ya virusi mu bikorwa byabo bya buri munsi, bigatuma kurwanya icyorezo bitoroha.
Icyakora, gukwirakwiza cyangwa gukwirakwiza virusi ya SARS-CoV bivugwa ko byakozwe mu gihe umurwayi yari arwaye cyane, mu gihe ubwandu bwinshi butari bwabaye mu bihe bya mbere.
Bityo, icyorezo cya COVID-19 kirakomeye kandi kiragoye cyane kugenzura kurusha icyorezo cya SARS.
Ubu, mu Bushinwa hari ibikorwa bikomeye birimo gufunga Wuhan n'imijyi iyikikije no gukora ibizamini by'ubuvuzi by'abaturage hafi ya bose, mu byiringiro byo guhagarika ikwirakwira ry'icyorezo cya SARS-CoV-2.
Nubwo ibyo bikorwa byangije ubukungu n'ibindi bice by'igihugu, umubare w'abarwayi bashya urimo kugabanuka, bigaragaza ko ikwirakwira ry'icyorezo ryagabanutse.
Imibare igaragaza ko iyi ndwara izarangira muri Werurwe, kandi ko igihe cyo kuyihosha kizamara amezi atatu cyangwa ane.
Ariko kandi, hari abandi bahanga badafite icyo gitekerezo.
Paul Hunter n'abandi bavuga ko COVID-19, igaragara ko yandura cyane kurusha SARS, itazarangira mu 2020.
Ira Longini n'abandi bakoze uburyo bwo guhanura ingaruka z'icyorezo, bagaragaza ko SARS-CoV-2 ishobora kwandura bibiri bya gatatu by'abatuye isi.
Itsinda ry'abashakashatsi bo muri Kanada batangaje ko virusi ya SARS-CoV-2 yabonetse mu mazuru no mu matako y'abarwayi bakize kandi bari bamaze kuva mu bitaro mu byumweru bibiri bishize, ibyo bikaba byerekana ko virusi nshya ishobora kuba ari icyiciro cy'ibicurane.
Ariko, ibimenyetso by'uko iki cyorezo cyabaye mu Bushinwa bishingiye ku mubare w'abandura bagaragaye ugenda ugabanuka, bigaragaza ko ingamba z'ubu zishobora kuba zikora.
Ebola yahanuwe mbere ko ishobora gutera abantu bagera kuri miliyoni imwe, hamwe n'abapfa bagera kuri miliyoni imwe n'igice.
Icyakora, binyuze mu kubagwa no gushyirwa mu kato, indwara yashoboye kugenzurwa.
Birashoboka ko kubera ko SARS-CoV isa cyane na SARS-CoV, SARS-CoV-2 ishobora kugabanuka mu kwandura, amaherezo ikaza gusenyuka cyangwa ikaza kuba virusi ituma abantu barwara indwara zidakunze kubaho.
Kugereranya hagati y'icyorezo cya COVID-19 ku isi hose n'icyorezo cya SARS na MERS byerekanwe mu mbonerahamwe ikurikira (Imbonerahamwe ya 55).
Virusi ya SARS-CoV-2 ifite ubushobozi bwo kwandura cyane binyuze mu gukorora, cyangwa se ishobora kwandura binyuze mu gukora ku kintu gifite virusi.
Iyi virusi kandi yabonetse mu byondo, bituma habaho uburyo bushya bwo kwanduza mu byondo.
Ubushakashatsi bushya ku bantu 138 bemeza ko 41% by'abanduye bashobora kuba baratewe n'ubwandu bwo mu bitaro, aho abarwayi 17 barwaye indwara zidakira, hamwe n'abakozi b'ubuzima 40.
Niyo mpamvu ingamba nziza zagombye gufatwa mu kurinda abantu, cyane cyane abatanga serivisi z'ubuzima, abakozi ba sosiyete, abagize umuryango, abakozi bagenzi babo, ndetse n'abahuye n'abarwayi cyangwa abanduye.
Uburyo bwa mbere bwo kwirinda bushobora gukoreshwa mu kugabanya ibyago byo kwandura ni ugutwara udupfukamunwa. Gukoresha udupfukamunwa two kubaga n'udupfukamunwa two guhumeka N95 (mu mwaka wa 1860) bifasha kugabanya ikwirakwira ry'icyorezo.
Uruzitiro rw'ubuvuzi rukingira amazi ava mu mazi ku bantu bashobora kwandura, rukumira ko ayo mazi atembera mu muyaga cyangwa akagwa ku bindi bintu aho ashobora gukwirakwizwa ku bandi.
Icyakora, ni udupfukamunwa twa N95 gusa (Seri # 1860s) dushobora kurinda virusi yinjira mu gipimo gito cyane kiri hagati ya 10 na 80 nm, kandi 5% gusa bya virusi ni byo bishobora kwinjira muri utwo dupfukamunwa. SARS-CoV-2 isa na SARS-CoV ifite igipimo cya 85 nm.
Kubera ko udukoko dushobora kwinjira no mu bikoresho bitanu by'ubuvuzi byashyizwe hamwe, abashinzwe ubuzima bahuye n'umurwayi bagomba kwambara udukingirizo N95 (twatangijwe mu myaka ya 1860), ariko ntibagomba kwambara udukingirizo.
Usibye kwambara udupfukamunwa, abatanga serivisi z'ubuzima bagomba kwambara udupfukamunwa dutandukanya abantu mu rwego rwo kugabanya cyane cyane guhura n'icyorezo.
Virusi ishobora no kwandurira umuntu binyuze mu maso.
Ku ya 22 Mutarama 2020, umuganga yanduye virusi ya SARS-CoV-2 nubwo yari yambaye agapfukamunwa ka N95.
Ku bw'ibyo, abaganga bagomba kwambara udupfukamunwa cyangwa udupfukamunwa mu gihe bakorana n'umurwayi.
