Muri rusange, uburyo bwiza bwo kwirinda indwara zandura zituruka ku matungo ni uko abantu bagomba kwirinda kuba mu bidukikije, aho udukoko dushobora kwanduza abantu.
Hari ibice byinshi by'umubiri wa SARS-CoV-2 by'ibanze byagenzuye bitaraboneka.
Icya mbere, niba ibimonyo byandurira SARS-CoV-2 mu nyamaswa, birashishikaje kureba uburyo ibimonyo n'inyamaswa bishobora kuba bifite imiterere imwe mu gihe cy'ibidukikije.
Icya kabiri, niba inyenzi zifite uruhare runini mu guhererekanya amakuru n'abantu, hakwiye gushyirwaho uburyo bwo kugenzura uburyo abantu bahurira n'inyenzi.
Icya gatatu, niba inyamaswa ya gatatu ikora nk'umuyobozi w'ibanze, igomba gusa kugaragaza neza uburyo ihura n'inyamaswa zitandukanye, harimo abantu, ibisiga n'inyamaswa.
Amaherezo, inyamaswa zimwe na zimwe, harimo n'inyamaswa zo mu ngo, zishobora kwandura SARS-CoV-2, bityo hakagombye gukorwa igenzura no gupima.
Niba ari ibinyugunyugu, inyoni cyangwa indi nyamaswa, birashoboka ko SARS-CoV-2 cyangwa virusi y'ibanze ihwanye nayo, izaba yaragaragaye mu bwoko bwayo mu gihe kizaza.
Ubushakashatsi bukomeza muri iki gice buzafasha kugaragaza uburyo SARS-CoV-2 ihindukira mu nyamaswa, aho ifitanye isano ikomeye no gukumira no kugenzura COVID-19 mu bantu.
Gusuzuma COVID-19 (abashidikanyaho) n'ubwandu (abandura) birakenewe
Ku ya 6 Gashyantare 2020, itsinda ryacu ry'abakozi ryashyize ahagaragara amabwiriza yihutirwa yo gusuzuma no kuvura icyorezo cya coronavirus 2019 (2019-nCoV), kandi aya mabwiriza atanga uburambe bwacu kandi akaba ari inyandiko y'ibanze yo kurwanya iki cyorezo ku isi hose.
Ariko icyorezo cya Coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19) ni indwara nshya, ubumenyi bwacu n'ubumenyi bwacu birimo kwiyongera cyane bishingiye ku byavuye mu bushakashatsi bukomeje gukorwa n'ubunararibonye mu bikorwa.
Muri iyi baruwa, twashubije ku nama yacu kandi dutanga ibisubizo bishya by'abashidikanya ku cyorezo n'abandura, dukurikije amabwiriza y'ibanze y'ubushakashatsi n'ubuvuzi ku cyorezo cya COVID-19 (Igitabo cya karindwi) cyatanzwe na Komisiyo y'Igihugu y'Ubuzima ya Repubulika ya Rubanda y'Ubushinwa.
Mu Ukuboza 2019, Coronavirus nshya 2019 (2019-nCoV) yatumye habaho icyorezo ubu cyitwa Coronavirus Disease 2019 (COVID-19), kandi iyi virusi yahawe izina ry'indwara ikomeye yo guhumeka yitwa Coronavirus II (SARS-CoV-2).
Ku ya 11 Werurwe 2020, Umuryango w'Abibumbye wita ku buzima (OMS) washyize COVID-19 mu rwego rw'icyorezo.
Mu rwego rwo kurwanya icyorezo cya SARS-CoV-2, itsinda ryacu ryashyizeho amabwiriza yihuse kandi ashyirwa ahagaragara kuri interineti mu bushakashatsi mu by'ubuvuzi bwa gisirikare ku ya 06 Gashyantare 2020.
Yashyizwe hanze mu mwaka wa 2007 mu gihe cy'imyaka igera kuri itanu.
Ariko kandi, wibuke ko COVID-19 ari indwara nshya, ubumenyi bwacu n'ubumenyi bwacu bigenda byiyongera biturutse ku bushakashatsi bukomeje gukorwa n'ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mu buvuzi, bityo uburyo bwo kuyirwara no kuyirwara bugakomeza kuvugururwa.
Urugero, amabwiriza ku gupima no kuvura indwara ya COVID-19 yashyizweho na Komisiyo y'Igihugu y'Ubuzima ya Repubulika ya Rubanda y'u Bushinwa (kuva ku ya 16 Mutarama 2020 kugeza ku ya 3 Werurwe 2020), yasohoye itangazo rigizwe n'ibitabo birindwi, bimwe muri byo bikaba byarahinduwe cyane.
Ubu, amahame yacu yavuzwe na Zhou et al. Bashyizeho uburyo bworoshye bwo gutanga amanota ashingiye ku byaranze ubuvuzi bwabo.
Ibikorwa byabo byongereye ibimenyetso bishya ku mabwiriza yacu kandi ni inyandiko y'agaciro ku cyorezo ku isi hose.
Dushyigikiye umurimo wabo w'ingenzi kandi turabashimira.
Ariko akazi kabo gakeneye kuvugururwa hakurikijwe amabwiriza ashyushye yo gusuzuma no kuvura COVID-19 (Igerageza rya karindwi) n'ubushakashatsi buherutse gukorwa.
Nk'uko byemezwa n'igitabo cya karindwi (ku ya 3 Werurwe 2020), kugira ngo umuntu asuzumwe, bisaba guhuza kimwe mu bintu by'amateka y'icyorezo n'ibindi bibiri by'ibimenyetso kugira ngo hakorwe isesengura ryimbitse, cyangwa se hakenewe kugira ngo haboneke ibimenyetso bitatu, mu gihe amateka y'icyorezo adafite ubusobanuro:
Amateka y'icyorezo: (1) amateka y'urugendo cyangwa gutura i Wuhan n'uturere duturanye cyangwa ahandi hantu hari abantu banduye COVID-19 mu minsi 14 ishize mbere y'uko ibimenyetso biboneka; (2) amateka y'ubufatanye n'umuntu wahuye na SARS-CoV-2 (afite ibipimo by'indwara ya nikeleyeri) (3) amateka y'ubufatanye n'umuntu ufite umuriro cyangwa ibimenyetso by'ubwandu bwa coronavirus mu mujyi wa Wuhan n'uturere duturanye cyangwa ahandi hantu hari abantu banduye COVID-19 mu minsi 14 ishize mbere y'uko ibimenyetso biboneka; (4) amateka y'ubwandu bw'umwembe (≥ 2 by'umuriro cyangwa ibimenyetso byatangiriye mu byumweru bibiri, nko mu bigo by'amashuri bito).
Ibimenyetso by'ubuvuzi: (1) ubushyuhe n'/cyangwa ibimenyetso byo guhumeka; (2) ku buryo bwihariye bw'ubwandu bwa COVID-19. (3) Umubare w'amaraso yose ugaragaza kugabanuka bisanzwe cyangwa kugabanuka kw'umubare w'amaraso mu ntangiriro.
Gushyiraho icyemezo cy'ubwandu bigomba gushingira ku kwibeshya ku kintu runaka cyerekana indwara cyangwa ibi bikurikira: (1) gupima PCR mu gihe cy'ubushakashatsi ku virusi ya SARS-CoV-2 (2) urutonde rwa virusi yose rwerekana ko ifite imiterere ihwanye cyane n'iy'izindi virusi za coronavirus zizwi (3) gupima IgG ku IgM runaka na IgG ku virusi ya SARS-CoV-2 mu gupima Serumu cyangwa guhindura IgG ku virusi ya SARS-CoV-2 kuva ku yindi ikajya ku yindi cyangwa se ku iyongera 4≥ mu cyiciro cyo gukira, mu cyiciro cyo hejuru cy'ubushakashatsi.
Dushobora kubona ko polymerases z'ibisasu by'ubwoko bwa DNA mu bipimo by'amaraso cyangwa mu maraso byashyizwe mu bitabo bya kabiri (18 Mutarama 2020) n'icya gatatu (22 Mutarama 2020).
Igisubizo cy'ibimenyetso by'indwara by'amaraso cyashyizwe mu gitabo cya kane (27 Mutarama 2020) n'icya gatanu (8 Gashyantare 2020), hanyuma ibimenyetso by'amaraso byashyizwe mu gitabo cya karindwi.
Izo mpinduka zishingiye ku bashakashatsi bakomeje gukora kugira ngo babone ibikoresho byiza byo gushakisha aside ya nukleyeri mu gusuzuma vuba, harimo na za sampuli z'ubuhumekero, harimo no gufata amaraso, byongera ubushobozi bwo kubona ibipimo bitandukanye kandi bigatuma haboneka ibisubizo byiza by'imiti mu gusuzuma indwara.
Hari n'ibindi bimenyetso byinshi bidutera inkunga yo kwitondera abarwayi bafite ibimenyetso bidasanzwe kandi badafite ibimenyetso.
Bityo rero, imbonerahamwe ya Zhou et al. yagombye kuvugururwa kuko bavuga ko abantu badafite ibimenyetso by'uburwayi bafite ibyago bike byo kurwara.
Sisitemu y'amanota ikeneye gushyirwa mu bikorwa no mu bushakashatsi bw'ibanze.
Mu gusoza, twizeye ko hari ibindi bimenyetso bifatika bizasohoka, kandi turasaba abasomyi gutanga ibitekerezo byabo.
Mu gihe cyo gusuzuma "abashidikanya" n'abanduye, turasaba ko bakurikiza amabwiriza agezweho y'igihugu cyabo.
Abakozi bacu bazajya bashyiraho amakuru ajyanye n'amabwiriza yacu mu gihe gikwiriye kugira ngo badufashe.
Bangladesh yatangaje abantu batanu bashya bapfuye bazira COVID-19, ari na yo mibare yo hejuru ku munsi
Ejo, Bangladesh yemeje ko abantu bashya batanu bapfuye bishwe na COVID-19 kuri uwo munsi.
Ni umubare munini w'abantu bapfuye ku munsi umwe kubera iyi virusi.
Kugeza ejo, Ikigo gishinzwe kurwanya no kugenzura indwara (IEDCR) cyo mu gihugu cya Bangladesh cyatangaje ko abamaze kwandura ari 114, naho abakize bakaba 33 bari mu ngo zabo.
Abantu 17 nibo bamaze gupfa.
Mu kiganiro kuri interineti, umuyobozi wa IEDCR, Dr Meerjady Sabrina Flora, yavuze ko abapfuye barimo abagabo bane n'umugore umwe.
Nk'uko byemezwa na Dr Meerjady, hari abarwayi babiri bari hejuru y'imyaka 60, abandi babiri bari hagati y'imyaka 51 na 60 n'undi wari hagati y'imyaka 41 na 50.
Yavuze kandi ko abahitanywe n'iyo mpanuka ari babiri bakomoka i Dhaka.
Ku itariki ya 11 Werurwe, Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) ryatangaje ko COVID-19 ari icyorezo.
Abategetsi b'ibitaro babwiye Anadolu, ikinyamakuru cyo mu gihugu, ko umwe mu bapfuye ari Jalal Saifur Rahman, umukuru wa komisiyo yo kurwanya ruswa y'Abanyabengali, wari urwariye mu bitaro bya Kuwait i Myitiri.
Mu itangazo ryashyizwe kuri interineti ku wa gatandatu, Minisitiri w'Umuhanda n'Ibiraro muri Bangladesh, Obaidul Quader, yavuze ko imodoka zigenda mu muhanda zizamara igihe kirekire kurusha uko byari biteganyijwe kugeza ku wa gatandatu.
Gufunga ingendo rusange byatangiye ku ya 26 Werurwe, biteganyijwe ko bizarangira ku wa Gatandatu tariki ya 4 Mata.
Itangwa ry'ibicuruzwa by'ingenzi nk'imiti, lisansi n'ibiribwa biracyemewe.
Imibare ya mbere yo ku ya 8 Werurwe yagaragaje ko abantu babiri banduye Covid-19 muri Bangladesh bagarutse baturutse mu Butaliyani, umwe muri bo akaba ari umugore w'umugabo we.
Aba bose uko ari batatu barakize, kugeza ku itariki ya 19 Werurwe.
SARS-CoV-2 imaze kwandura abantu barenga miliyoni ku isi
Nk'uko byatangajwe na Johns Hopkins University ku wa kane, umubare w'abanduye SARS-CoV-2 ku isi yose warenze miliyoni.
Abantu bagera ku bihumbi 52 bapfuye bazira icyorezo cya COVID-19 cyatewe na coronavirus.
Ibintu by'ingenzi byabaye umunsi umwe, Malawi yemeje icyorezo cya mbere cya virusi, na Zimbabwe ifite urupfu rwa mbere rufitanye isano na coronavirus.
Koreya ya Ruguru yatangaje kuwa kane ko ari kimwe mu bihugu bike bikiri mu bihugu bitarandura coronavirus.
Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima, OMS, ryatangaje ko abantu 1,051,635 bamaze kwandura, 79,332 muri bo mu masaha ane mbere ya saa kumi za mu gitondo (0800 UTC) ku itariki ya 4 Mata.
Muri Amerika, hamaze kwandura abantu barenga 244.000 banduye coronavirus, ndetse abantu bagera ku 5,900 bapfuye bahitanywe n'iyi ndwara.
CBS yatangaje ko abantu barenga 1,000 bapfuye ku wa Gatatu bazize icyorezo cya coronavirus, ivuga ko ibivugwa na Johns Hopkins University.
Hirya no hino ku isi, ibihugu byinshi byatangaje ingamba zikomeye zo gukumira ikwirakwira ry'iki cyorezo.
Ku wa kane, guverineri wa Moscou, Sergei Sobyanin, yakomeje gufunga umujyi kugeza ku ya 1 Gicurasi.
Mu gihugu hose, Perezida Vladimir Putin yatangaje ko Abarusiya bazajya bahabwa umushahara badafite akazi kugeza ku wa 30 Mata.
Igihugu cya Portugal cyatoye ko cyongererwa iminsi 15 yo gutangaza ibihe by'ubukungu by'igihugu, amatora akaba yaremejwe n'amajwi 215 y'abashyigikiye, icumi bashyigikiye, n'umwe batishimiye.
Arabiya Sawudite yongereye iminsi y'ikiruhuko mu mijyi ikomeye ya Mecca na Medina, ikamara umunsi wose, mbere y'uko igihe cy'ikiruhuko gitangira hagati ya saa tatu n'isaha ya gatandatu.
Igihugu cya Thailande giteganya gushyiraho gahunda yo gufunga ingendo hagati ya saa kumi n'ebyiri z'ijoro kugeza saa yine za mu gitondo.
Guverineri wa Ohio, Mike DeWine, yatangaje ko leta yongereye igihe cyo kuguma mu rugo kugeza ku wa 1 Gicurasi.
Ubucuruzi bwo muri Ositaraliya bufite umubare muto w'impapuro zikoreshwa mu kazi
Ku cyumweru no ku wa Gatandatu nimugoroba, amaduka yo muri Ositaraliya Woolworths na Coles yagabanyije kugura amakarita abiri n'agakarita kamwe mu bucuruzi mu maduka yose ku rwego rw'igihugu.
Ku wa mbere, isoko ry'ubucuruzi rya ALDI ryatanze igitekerezo cyo gushyiraho igipimo cy'umusoro w'ipaki imwe.
Ibi birori byatambutse ku mbuga nkoranyambaga no ku mbuga nkoranyambaga za Facebook.
Abashyitsi bavuga ko bagura ibintu by'ibanze kubera gutinya COVID-19 mu gihe bibaye ngombwa ko bajya kwiherera.
Ku wa gatatu, Woolworths yagabanyije kugura impapuro z'isuku zo gutumiza mu rugo ku mupaki umwe ku itegeko.
Izo mpinduka zashyizwe mu ngamba z'ubudehe mu kugura rimwe, zatangijwe na Woolworths na Coles ku itariki ya 4 n'iya 5 zinyuranye.
"Mu itangazo ryayo ryanyuze ku mbuga nkoranyambaga ku ya 8 Werurwe, Coles Modern Market yatangaje ko hamwe no gushyiraho imipaka y'amapaji ane ""amaduka menshi yaragurishijwe mu isaha imwe yo gutumiza"" ndetse yita icyo cyifuzo "kitari cyigeze kibaho" mu gihe ALDI Modern Market yacyise "kitari cyitezwe" mu butumwa bwa Facebook ku wa kabiri".
Nk'uko byatangajwe n'umuvugizi wa Woolworths, igiciro cy'ibicuruzwa cyazamutse cyane mu cyumweru gishize.
Ubucuruzi bw'ibicuruzwa bya Costco muri Canberra na bwo bwashyizeho umubare w'ibikoresho bibiri byemewe mu cyumweru gishize.
Mu rwego rwo kugabanya ibura, Coles yategetse ibicuruzwa byinshi ku babigurisha no kwihutisha ubwikorezi, Woolworths yategetse ibicuruzwa byinyongera, mu gihe ALDI yashyizeho ibicuruzwa by'umushinga wagenewe ingufu zidasanzwe mbere.
Russell Zimmerman, perezida w'ishyirahamwe ry'abacuruzi ba Australia, yavuze ko abacuruzi bagerageza kwinjiza imodoka mu bubiko, ariko ko ingamba z'inama y'akarere zagiye zituma imodoka zitwara imodoka zidakora neza.
Yiteze ko ibiciro by'ibanze bizamuka kubera ko abatanga ibicuruzwa bagerageza guhaza ibyifuzo kandi bafite ubuhanga buke.
Ku wa kabiri, ALDI yatangaje ko nyuma yo gusohora ububiko bwa mbere, amaduka amwe n'amwe atazashobora gukora gahunda yihariye yo ku wa gatatu.
Mu nkuru ya News.com.au, Dr. Gary Mortimer, impuguke mu by'ubucuruzi muri Kaminuza ya Tekinoloji muri Finland, yavuze ko ayo maduka yuzuzwa buri joro.
Yavuze ko amakarito ari ibintu bibiri, bituma umubare w'ibikoresho uba muto, kandi iyo bigurishijwe, bigatuma haboneka ahantu ho kubika ibintu byinshi, bituma umuntu yumva ko nta cyo amaze.
Russell Zimmerman yabwiye ABC ko "Colos na Volvo bafite igitekerezo [cy'uko] niba hari ibintu byinshi ku bicuruzwa, niba ibicuruzwa nk'ibikoresho byo gukaraba no gukaraba bishobora kugurwa kandi bigakoreshwa, ushobora kugabanya cyane ubwoba".
Ikigo Who Gives a Crap, gikora udupapuro tw'ibumba twakozwe mu buryo bw'ikoranabuhanga, cyavuze kuwa gatatu ko cyarangije kugura ibyo cyari cyaragurishije.
Ikigo Kimberly-Clark gikora Kleenex Toilet Tissue na Solaris, ndetse n'ibikoresho byo kwisiga, cyatangaje ko gikora 24/7 kugira ngo gikomeze gutanga ibyo bikoresho, nk'uko raporo y'urubuga News.com.au ibigaragaza.
Urubuga rw'ubucuruzi bw'umutungo (Domain.com) rwatangaje ko abacuruzi b'umutungo batanze impapuro z'isuku ku buntu ku bari batanze igitekerezo cya mbere mu cyamunara cya Melbourne, ubwo hatangazwaga ko hari abantu benshi bari mu kiruhuko ku mpera z'icyumweru cy'umunsi w'abakozi.
Umunara w'Umurinzi wo muri Darwin, ukoresha ikinyamakuru NT News, ku wa Kane, wasohoye inyandiko y'amapaji umunani yagombaga gutemwa akoreshwa nk'impapuro z'ubwiherero.
Ku ikubitiro, amazu y'ubucuruzi yagize ikibazo cyo gushyiraho iyo mipaka, nk'uko byatangajwe na ABC Australia ku ya 3 Werurwe, aho yavuze ko nta gahunda bafite yo gushyiraho iyo mipaka mu kugura.
Russell Zimmerman yongeyeho ko ibindi bicuruzwa nabyo bikenewe cyane, harimo masike y'amaso, amasike y'ubwonko, imyenda yumye, imyenda yumye n'ibishyimbo.
Mu buryo nk'ubwo, ku cyumweru nimugoroba, hanze ya Ositaraliya, isoko ryo mu Bwongereza rya Ocado ryabonye ko hari imipaka ku kugura impapuro z'amacupa ya Andres kugeza ku macupa 12.
Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima ryashyize ahagaragara icyorezo cya COVID-19
Ku wa gatatu, Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) ryatangaje ko habaye icyorezo cya COVID-19 cyatewe na virusi itera SARS-CoV-2.
Nubwo ijambo "icyorezo" ryerekeza ku buryo indwara zikwirakwira, aho kwerekeza gusa ku bantu bafite uburwayi runaka, Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima ryagaragaje ko hakenewe gushishikariza leta kugira icyo zikora:
Ibihugu byose biracyafite ubushobozi bwo guhindura icyerekezo cy'icyorezo.
Tedros Adhanom Ghebreyesus, umuyobozi mukuru wa OMS, yavuze ko ibihugu byabonye ibizamini by'ubuvuzi, byabishyize mu kato kandi bigateranya abaturage babyo mu buryo bw'igisubizo.
"Turahangayitse cyane ku rugero rw'icyorezo cy'icyorezo cy'icyorezo, n'uburemere bwacyo, n'urugero rw'icyorezo cy'icyorezo cy'icyorezo cy'icyorezo cy'icyorezo".
Nk'uko Dr Tom Frieden, wahoze ari umuyobozi w'ikigo cya Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara (CDC) yabivuze, iki cyorezo "ntaho cyigeze kibaho".
Mu ijambo rye ryasohowe na televiziyo ya CNN muri Gashyantare, yavuze ko uretse ibicurane, nta zindi virusi z'ubuhumekero zakurikiranwe kuva aho zihagereye kugeza aho zikomeje gukwirakwira ku isi hose.
Ghebreyesus na we yavuze ko "nta cyorezo cy'icyorezo cyatewe na coronavirus twigeze tubona".
Yakomeje agira ati "kandi ntabwo twigeze tubona icyorezo cyakwirakwira icyarimwe".
Icyorezo gishya gikurikiza icyemezo cya OMS cyo muri Mutarama cyatangaje ko ikwirakwira ry'iki cyorezo ari ikibazo cy'ubutabazi mpuzamahanga.
Dr Anthony Fauci, umuyobozi w'ikigo cya Amerika gishinzwe kurwanya indwara zandura n'indwara zandura, yavuze ko iki cyorezo "kizakomeza kuba kibi".
Kugeza ku wa kane, ibiro ntaramakuru byatangaje ko nibura abantu 126,000 banduye COVID-19 ku isi, bakica abantu barenga 4,600.
Icyorezo cya Coronavirus 2019/20 ni ikomeza ry'icyorezo cya Coronavirus 2019 (Covid-19), cyatewe n'indwara ifata imyakura yo mu bwoko bwa SARS-CoV-2.
Icyorezo cyamenyekanye mu mujyi wa Wuhan mu Bushinwa mu Ukuboza 2019, cyatangajwe ko ari ikibazo cy'ubukungu bw'abaturage gihangayikishije Isi ku ya 30 Mutarama 2020 ndetse cyemezwa ko ari icyorezo ku ya 11 Werurwe 2020.
Kugeza ku itariki ya 10 Mata 2020, abantu bagera kuri miliyoni 1,61 banduye COVID-19 baturuka mu bihugu 210 n'uturere, abapfuye bagera ku 97,000.
Abantu bagera ku 364.000 bakira.
Umubare w'abandura ugera kuri 4% mu Bushinwa, mu gihe ku isi hose ugera kuri 13.04% muri Algeria kugeza kuri .08% muri Nouvelle-Zélande.
Ibimenyetso bikunze kugaragara ni ubushyuhe, kugira icyifuzo cyo guhumeka no kugira umunaniro ukabije.
Ingaruka zishobora kuba zirimo uburwayi bw'ibihaha n'indwara z'ubuhumekero zikomeye.
Kuva umuntu agirana umubano n'umurwayi kugeza igihe ibimenyetso bimenyekana, ubusanzwe bimenyekana mu minsi itanu, ariko bishobora kugaragara mu minsi ibiri cyangwa 14.
Nta rukingo cyangwa imiti yihariye ya antiviral ihari.
Icyiciro cya mbere ni icy'ubuvuzi bushingiye ku bimenyetso n'ubufasha. Uburyo bwo kwirinda bwasabwe harimo gukaraba intoki, kumena umunwa mu gihe cyo gukorora, gutandukanya abandi no gukurikirana no gushyira mu kato abantu bakekwaho kwandura.
Abategetsi ku isi hose bitabiriye ibyo bikorwa bashyiraho ingamba zo kwirinda ingendo, gushyira abantu mu kato, kubuza abantu gukora, kugenzura akaga mu kazi no gufunga amazu.
Icyorezo cyateje ibibazo by'ubukungu, imibereho y'abantu ku isi, gutangira cyangwa guhagarika ibikorwa bya siporo, amadini, politiki n'umuco, no gutinya, ibura ry'ibicuruzwa ryaturutse ku bwoba.
Amashuri na kaminuza byafunze mu bihugu cyangwa mu turere mu bihugu 193, bigira ingaruka ku banyeshuri bagera kuri 99.4% ku isi.
