Tayiwani, imaze gukora udupfukamunwa tw'amabuye y'agaciro miriyoni icumi ku munsi kuva mu kwezi kwa gatatu, yasabye abagenzi mu modoka n'amagare y'abasifuzi kwambara udupfukamunwa ku ya 1 Mata.
Panama yasabye ko abantu bambara udupfukamunwa igihe cyose bavuye mu rugo, ndetse yanasabye ko abantu badashobora kugura udupfukamunwa bakora ku ntoki.
Amasasu akoreshwa cyane mu Buyapani, Koreya y'Epfo, Maleziya na Singapuru.
Kwitarura abandi (cyangwa se kwitarura abandi) bikubiyemo ingamba zo kugabanya ubwandu mu buryo butuma indwara idakwirakwira cyane, mu gihe abantu badahuza imibonano.
Uburyo bwo kubikora harimo gushyira abantu mu kato, kugabanya ingendo no gufunga amashuri, aho bakorera, ibibuga by'imikino, inganda cyangwa amazu y'ubucuruzi.
Umuntu ku giti cye ashobora gukoresha uburyo bwo kwirinda mu buryo bw'ikoranabuhanga, akomeza kuguma mu rugo, kugabanya ingendo, kwirinda ahantu hahurira abantu benshi, gusabana nta cyo akoreye abandi no kwirinda kwihererana.
Ubu, leta nyinshi zirimo gushyiraho cyangwa gushyiraho amabwiriza yo kwirinda mu turere twugarijwe n'icyorezo.
Ubunini bw'ikoraniro ryihariye bwasabwe n'inzego za leta n'imiryango y'ubuzima ya Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika, bwagabanyijwe mu buryo bwihuse buva ku bantu 250 (niba nta cyorezo cya COVID-19 cyakwirakwiriye mu karere) bujya kuri 50, nyuma buza ku bantu 10.
Ku ya 22 Werurwe 2020, Ubudage bwabujije amateraniro rusange y'abantu babiri cyangwa barenga. Abantu bakuru n'abafite indwara zirimo diyabete, indwara z'umutima, indwara z'ubuhumekero, indwara z'umurindi w'amaraso n'uburwayi bw'ubwirinzi bw'umubiri, bafite ibyago byinshi byo kurwara indwara zikomeye kandi bafite ingaruka nyinshi. Mu mpera za Werurwe 2020, Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima n'andi mashyirahamwe y'ubuzima yatangiye gukoresha imvugo "kwikurura mu buryo bw'umubiri" asimbuza "kurinda umubiri" kugira ngo agaragaze ko intego ari ukugabanya ubukana bw'umubiri mu gihe bakomeza kugirana imishyikirano ya hafi cyangwa kure.
Gukoresha ijambo "kwishyira ukizana" byagize ingaruka zo gutuma abantu bakomeza kwiherera mu buryo bwuzuye aho kubashishikariza gukomeza gushyikirana n'abandi mu bundi buryo. Abayobozi bamwe batangaje amabwiriza y'ubuzima bw'imyororokere yo gukoresha mu gihe cy'icyorezo.
Muri byo harimo inama yo gukora imibonano mpuzabitsina gusa n'abo mubana badafite virusi cyangwa ibimenyetso bya virusi.
Kwigumira mu rugo ni inama ku bantu basanganywe COVID-19 n'abakekwaho kuyandura.
Abashinzwe ubuzima batangaje amabwiriza arambuye yo kwigunga mu buryo bukwiriye. Leta nyinshi zategetse cyangwa zasabye ko abantu bose baba mu turere twanduye bicwa n'icyorezo.
Inama yo kwitandukanya n'abandi yatangajwe ku bantu bari mu byiciro by'ibyago byinshi.
Abantu bashobora kuba barahuye n'umuntu ufite COVID-19 n'abaherutse kujya mu gihugu cyangwa akarere kagize ubwandu bukabije basabwe kwiyicarira mu gihe cy'iminsi 14 uhereye igihe haherukaga kugaragara.
Uburyo bwo kurwanya iki cyorezo ni ukugenzura, gukumira no kugabanya ubukana bwacyo.
Ibi bikorwa mu bihe bya mbere by'icyorezo, bigamije gukurikirana no gushyira mu kato abanduye, no gushyiraho ubundi buryo bwo kugenzura, gukwirakwiza no gukingira kugira ngo indwara ihagarare mu baturage bose.
Iyo hatagize ubushobozi bwo gukumira ikwirakwira ry'icyorezo, imihati ikurikiraho iba igera ku cyiciro cyo kugabanya: ingamba zifatwa zo kugabanya ikwirakwira ry'icyorezo no kugabanya ingaruka zacyo ku rwego rw'ubuzima n'imibereho myiza y'abaturage.
Mu gihe cy'imyaka myinshi, abantu benshi batangiye kugira ibibazo by'uburwayi, ariko hari n'abandi benshi batangiye kugira ibibazo by'uburwayi.
Gukumira bisaba ingamba zikomeye zo kwirinda icyorezo binyuze mu kugabanya umubare w'abacyandura ku kigero kiri munsi ya 1 ku ijana by'icyorezo, ikwirakwira ry'icyorezo rigerageza kugabanya ubukana bw'icyorezo, kizwi nka "icyorezo cy'icyorezo".
Ibi bigabanya ibyago byo kubura serivisi z'ubuzima kandi bigatuma haboneka igihe cyo gukora inkingo n'ubuvuzi.
Ubufasha butari ubuvuzi bushobora kugenzura iki cyorezo burimo ingamba zo kwirinda nk'ubushyuhe bw'ibishashi, kwambara agapfukamunwa no kwigunga, ingamba z'umuryango zigamije gukumira inzara, nko gufunga amashuri no guhagarika amateraniro manini.
Ibindi bihugu byashyizeho ingamba zitandukanye zigamije kugabanya ikwirakwira ry'icyorezo.
Koreya y'Epfo yakoze igenzura rikomeye no gushyira mu kato abantu ku rwego rw'igihugu, kandi itanga itangazo ku bijyanye n'imikorere y'abanduye.
Singapore yatanze inkunga y'amafaranga ku bantu banduye, ikora isuzuma kandi igatanga ibihano bikomeye ku batayikurikiza.
Muri Taiwan, hagabanyijwe inganda zikora udupfukamunwa n'ibihano ku bikoresho by'ubuvuzi.Ibimenyetso by'u Bwongereza na Amerika byerekana ko kugabanya (gukumira ariko kutahagarika ikwirakwira ry'icyorezo) no kucyirinda (kugabanya icyorezo) bifite imbogamizi zikomeye.
Politiki nziza yo kugabanya ishobora kugabanya ibyangombwa by'ubuvuzi ku kigero cya 2/3 n'urupfu ku kigero cya kabiri, ariko bigakomeza gutuma abantu babarirwa mu bihumbi amagana bapfa, kandi uburyo bwo kuvura bugenda bugabanuka.
Ingamba z'ibikorwa zishobora gutorwa kandi zigomba gushyirwa mu bikorwa igihe cyose virusi ikomeje gukwirakwira mu bantu (cyangwa kugeza igihe urukingo rubonetse, niba rwabayeho mbere), igihe ubwandu bwiyongera vuba mu gihe ingamba zisuzumwa.
Gufata ingamba z'igihe kirekire zo gukumira icyorezo byateje ingaruka mbi ku baturage no ku bukungu.
Nta muti wihariye wa virusi wahawe uburenganzira bwo gukoreshwa mu kuvura COVID-19, ariko ibikorwa byo kuwukora birakomeje, harimo no kugerageza imiti iboneka.
Gufata imiti irinda indwara, kunywa amazi no kuruhuka bishobora kugabanya ibimenyetso.
Bitewe n'uburemere bw'iyo ndwara, imiti ya ogisijeni, imiti yo mu mitsi no gufashwa guhumeka bishobora gukenerwa.
Gukoresha imiti ya Steroids bishobora gutuma ingaruka zirushaho kuba mbi.
Ingingo nyinshi zigeze kwemerwa mu kuvura izindi ndwara ziterwa na virusi zirimo gusuzumwa mu kuvura COVID-19.
OMS kandi yavuze ko imiti imwe n'imwe ikoreshwa mu buryo bwa gakondo n'ubw'iwabo ishobora gutanga ubudahangarwa ku bimenyetso by'ubwandu bwa SARS-CoV-19.
Kongera ubushobozi no guhindura uburyo bwo kwita ku buzima ku bantu banduye COVID-19 byasobanuwe n'ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima nk'uburyo bw'ibanze bwo gusubiza icyorezo.
ECDC na OMS mu Burayi batangaje ko ibitaro n'imikorere y'ubuvuzi byatangiye guhindura uburyo bwo gukoresha ibikoresho byinshi, harimo gushyira imbaraga mu kwipimisha COVID-19, guhagarika ingendo, guhitamo igihe gihagije cyo kwitandukanya no kwitandukanya, kongera ubushobozi bwo kwita ku barwayi ba COVID-19 binyuze mu gutoza abakozi no kongera ibikoresho byo guhumeka no gutura.
Hari ibitekerezo bitandukanye ku byerekeye aho icyorezo cya mbere (cyitwa "umurwayi wa zero") gishobora guturuka.
Umuntu wa mbere wamenyekanye ko afite virusi nshya kandi itandukanye ashobora kuba yaravutse ku itariki ya 1 Ukuboza 2019 mu mujyi wa Wuhan, mu ntara ya Hubei mu Bushinwa.
Mu gihe cy'ukwezi, umubare w'abanduye virusi ya Zika muri Hubei wariyongereye cyane.
Abenshi muri abo barwayi bari bafitanye isano n'isoko rya Huanan ryakundaga kugurisha ibiribwa by'inyanja, na ho hagurishwa inyamaswa nzima, kandi hari amakuru avuga ko virusi yavuye mu nyamaswa z'inyamaswa cyangwa se mu yandi magambo ko ikomoka ku nyamaswa.
Ku itariki ya 30 Ukuboza, abaganga bo mu bitaro bya Wuhan Central Hospital babwiye bagenzi babo ko SARS ari virusi imeze nka coronavirus.
Abaganga umunani barimo Li Wenliang, bashyizwe ku rutonde rw'abapolisi bashinjwa gutangaza ibinyoma, undi witwa Ai Fen, ashyirwa ku rutonde rw'abashinjwa guteza imvururu.
Komisiyo y'Ubuzima ya Wuhan nyuma yaho yasohoye itangazo ku mugaragaro ku wa 31 Ukuboza, imenyesha Umuryango w'Abibumbye wita ku buzima (OMS).
Abategetsi b'ubuzima muri Wuhan babwiwe ko hari umubare uhagije w'abantu banduye icyorezo cya pneumonia kitigeze kibaho, kugira ngo hatangwe iperereza mu ntangiriro za Mutarama.
Mu ntangiriro no hagati ya Mutarama 2020, virusi yageze mu zindi ntara zo mu Bushinwa, iterwa n'impunzi zagiye ziterana mu gihe cy'umunsi mukuru w'umwaka mushya w'Ubushinwa, kandi Wuhan ni umuhanda munini w'ingendo n'ingendo.
Ku ya 20 Mutarama, Ubushinwa bwatangaje ko hari abantu bashya bagera kuri 140 mu munsi umwe, barimo babiri mu mujyi wa Beijing n'undi umwe mu mujyi wa Shenzhen.
Nyuma y'aho, imibare y'ubutegetsi yagaragaje ko abantu 6,174 batangiye kugaragaza ibimenyetso ku itariki ya 20 Mutarama 2020. Ku itariki ya 26 Werurwe, Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika zari zimaze kurenga u Bushinwa n'u Butaliyani nk'igihugu gifite umubare munini w'abanduye ku isi. Ku itariki ya 9 Mata 2020, abantu barenga 1.61 miliyoni bari bamaze kwandura, abantu barenga 97,000 barapfuye, abandi barenga 364,000 barakira.
Mu bihugu n'uturere bigera kuri 200, nibura hari umuntu umwe wanduye.
Kubera icyorezo cyugarije Uburayi, ibihugu byinshi byo mu karere ka Schengen byagabanyije urujya n'uruza rw'abantu no gushyiraho igenzura ry'imipaka.
Igisubizo cy'igihugu cyaje gikubiyemo ingamba zo gukumira, nko gushyira abantu mu kato (byitwa gufungura mu rugo, gutegeka aho baba cyangwa gufunga urugi), no gufunga ingo, n'ibindi. Ku itariki ya 2 Mata, abantu bagera kuri miriyoni 300 cyangwa 90% by'abaturage bari mu kato muri Amerika, abantu barenga miriyoni 50 bari mu kato muri Filipine, abantu bagera kuri miriyoni 59 bari mu kato muri Afurika y'Epfo, n'abantu bagera kuri miriyari 1,3 bari mu kato mu Buhinde.
Ku ya 26 Werurwe, abantu bagera kuri miliyari 1.7 ku isi hose bari mu buryo bwo gufungirwa mu nzu, umubare wiyongereyeho miriyoni 2.6 mu minsi ibiri yakurikiyeho, ni ukuvuga kimwe cya gatatu cy'abatuye isi bose.
Umuntu wa mbere wemejwe ko arwaye COVID-19 yavutse ku itariki ya 1 Ukuboza 2019 mu mujyi wa Wuhan, kandi raporo itari yemewe igaragaza ko umuntu wa mbere wigeze kwandura by'agateganyo yavutse ku itariki ya 17 Ugushyingo.
Dr Zhang Jixian yakurikiranye icyiciro cy'abarwayi ba pneumonia y'inkomoko itazwi ku ya 26 Ukuboza, ibyo bitaro bye byabibwiye Wuhan Jianghan CDC ku ya 27 Ukuboza.
Ibizamini bya mbere byagenewe ibipimo by'umurwayi byakozwe ku ya 27 Ukuboza 2019 byerekanye ko hari virusi ya corona, nka SARS.
Itangazo rusange ryatanzwe na Komisiyo y'Ubuzima ya Wuhan ku wa 31 Ukuboza.
Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) ryamenyeshejwe kuri uwo munsi.
"Igihe ibyo bitangazamakuru byatangwaga, abaganga bo mu mujyi wa Wuhan bari barahawe umuburo n'abapolisi kubera ""kuvuga ibihuha" ku cyorezo".
Komisiyo y'ubuzima y'u Bushinwa yabanje kuvuga ko nta gihamya ifatika y'ubwandu buva ku muntu ujya ku wundi.
Mu mpera za Mutarama, leta y'Ubushinwa yatangije gahunda ikomeye nyuma yaho Xi Jinoing, Perezida wa Komisiyo y'Akarere ka China, yavuze ko ari "intambara y'abantu" yo kurwanya icyorezo.
Mu byasobanuwe ko ari "igikorwa gikomeye cyo guhagarika abantu mu mateka y'abantu", gufunga ingendo byatangajwe ku ya 23 Mutarama, bihagarika ingendo mu mujyi wa Wuhan no hanze yawo, byongerwa ku mijyi 15 yo muri Herbei, bikagira ingaruka ku baturage bagera kuri miliyoni 57.
Gukoresha imodoka bwite birabujijwe mu mujyi.
Umunsi mukuru w'umwaka mushya w'Ubushinwa (itariki 25 Mutarama) wasubitswe mu bice byinshi.
Abayobozi batangaje ko bagiye kubaka ibitaro by'imfatakibanza, ibitaro bya Huoshenshan byubatswe mu minsi 10.
Nyuma yaho, ikindi bitaro, Leishenshan Hospital, cyubatswe kugira ngo kijye kwakira abarwayi benshi.
Usibye ibitaro biherutse kubakwa, Ubushinwa bwahinduye ibindi bibuga 14 i Wuhan, nk'ibigo by'amakoraniro n'ibibuga by'imikino, ngo bibe ibitaro by'agateganyo.Ku ya 26 Mutarama, guverinoma yashyizeho ingamba zinyuranye zo guhangana n'ikwirakwira ry'icyorezo cya COVID-19, harimo gutanga itangazo ry'ubuzima ku bantu batembereza ndetse no gusubika iminsi mikuru ya Noheli.
Kaminuza n'amashuri hirya no hino mu gihugu na byo byafunzwe.
Akarere ka Hong Kong na Macau kagiye gatanga ingamba nyinshi cyane cyane ku mashuri na za kaminuza.
Ingamba zo gukora mu buryo bwa kure zashyizweho mu bice byinshi by'Ubushinwa.
Ibihano byo gutembera byemejwe imbere no hanze ya Hubei.
Itangazamakuru rya rubanda ryarasuzumwe, kandi inzu ndangamurage yo mu Bushinwa yafunzwe by'agateganyo.
"Gukwirakwiza urujya n'uruza rw'abantu byashyizwe mu bikorwa mu mijyi myinshi, kandi byemezwa ko abantu bagera kuri miliyoni 760 (abarenga kimwe cya kabiri cy'abaturage) bahanganye n'ubwoko runaka bwo gukingirwa hanze. Nyuma y'uko iki cyorezo cyinjiye mu cyiciro cyacyo cy'isi yose muri Werurwe, abategetsi b'Ubushinwa bashyizeho ingamba zikomeye zo gukumira virusi "iyinjira" iturutse mu bindi bihugu".
Urugero, Beijing yashyizeho iminsi 14 yo kwigunga ku bantu bose bari mu rugendo mpuzamahanga binjira mu mujyi. Ku itariki ya 23 Werurwe, mu Bushinwa honyine habonetse umuntu umwe wanduye mu gihe cy'iminsi itanu, umwe muri bo akaba yari umuturage wari uvuye i Istanbul ajya i Guangzhou.
Ku ya 24 Werurwe 2020, Minisitiri w'Intebe w'Ubushinwa, Li Keqiang, yatangaje ko ikwirakwira ry'ubwandu mu gihugu ryihagaritswe byimazeyo, kandi ko iki cyorezo cyagaragaye mu Bushinwa.
Mu minsi imwe gusa y'ibihano, ingendo zagabanyijwe muri Hubei, usibye Wuhan, nyuma y'amezi abiri hatangiye gufunga ingendo. Minisiteri y'ububanyi n'amahanga y'Ubushinwa yatangaje ku ya 26 Werurwe 2020 ko kwinjira ku bafite viza cyangwa ibyangombwa byo gutura bizaba byahagaritswe guhera ku ya 28 Werurwe, nta makuru arambuye yerekeranye n'igihe iyi gahunda izarangirira.
Abashaka kujya mu Bushinwa bagomba gusaba viza muri ambasade cyangwa muri konsula y'Ubushinwa.
Guverinoma y'u Bushinwa yashishikarije inganda n'inganda kongera gufungura ku itariki ya 30 Werurwe, kandi itanga inkunga y'amafaranga ku bigo by'ubucuruzi.Inama y'igihugu yatangaje umunsi wo gusezera, gutangira n'iminsi itatu y'agahenge ku rwego rw'igihugu saa kumi n'ebyiri z'umugoroba ku itariki ya 4 Mata, mu gihe na none ari umunsi mukuru w'amavuta, nubwo guverinoma y'igihugu yasabye imiryango kubahiriza konti yo kuri interineti mu kubahiriza isuku y'umubiri mu kwirinda icyorezo cya COVID-19.
COVID-19 yemejwe ko yakwirakwiriye muri Koreya y'Epfo ku ya 20 Mutarama 2020 iturutse mu Bushinwa.
Ikigo cy'igihugu gishinzwe ubuzima cyatangaje ko habonetse ubwandu bwinshi bwemejwe ku itariki ya 20 Gashyantare, ahanini buturutse ku ikoraniro ry'abayoboke b'idini ry'Aba-Yesu ryitwa Shincheonji i Daegu.
Abayoboke ba Shincheonji binjiye Daegu baturutse mu mujyi wa Wuhan bakekwaho kuba aribo batumye iki cyorezo gitangira.
Kugeza ku ya 22 Gashyantare, mu bantu 9.336 bafite idini, 1.261 cyangwa hafi 13% bari bafite ibimenyetso. Koreya yatangaje ko ikibazo cy'ubudehe cyageze ku rwego rwo hejuru ku ya 23 Gashyantare 2020.
Ku ya 28 Gashyantare, abasaga 2,000 bemejwe ko banduye muri Koreya, ku ya 29 Gashyantare bagera ku 3,150.
Inzego zose za gisirikare za Koreya y'Epfo zashyizwe mu kato nyuma y'uko abasirikare batatu bapimwe basanga bafite virusi.
Amategeko y'indege na yo yagize ingaruka, bityo arahinduka. Koreya y'Epfo yashyizeho gahunda ya mbere nini kandi iteguye ku isi yo kugenzura abaturage kugira ngo basangire virusi no gushyira mu kato abanduye, no gukurikirana no gukumira abanduye.
Uburyo bwo kugenzura, harimo kwiyitirira kugenzura ibimenyetso by'abashya bavuye mu mahanga hakoreshejwe porogaramu za terefone, gupima virusi ku munsi ukurikiyeho, no kongera ubushobozi bwo gupima, byemerera abantu gupima 20,000 buri munsi.
Porogaramu ya Koreya y'Epfo yafashwe nk'iy'ibanze mu kugenzura icyorezo, nubwo nta cyizere cyatanzwe ku mujyi wose.
Abanyakoreya benshi banditse amabaruwa y'ubutegetsi arimo amahitamo abiri: bashinja Moon ibyo bavuga ko leta ye itarimo gukemura neza icyorezo cyangwa bamushimira uko yabigenje.
Ku ya 23 Werurwe, byatangajwe ko Koreya y'Epfo ifite umubare muto w'abanduye buri munsi ugereranyije n'indi minsi mu byumweru bine bishize.
Ku ya 29 Werurwe, byatangajwe ko guhera ku ya 1 Mata, abantu bose bashya baje baturutse mu mahanga bazajya bahatirwa kumara ibyumweru bibiri mu kato.
Nk'uko byatangajwe n'itangazamakuru ku ya 1 Mata, Koreya y'Epfo yakiriye impapuro zisaba inkunga yo gupima virusi zivuye mu bihugu 121 bitandukanye.
Irani yatangaje ko icyorezo cya SARS-CoV-2 cyemejwe bwa mbere ku ya 19 Gashyantare mu mujyi wa Qom, aho abantu babiri bapfuye, nk'uko bitangazwa na Minisiteri y'Ubuzima n'Uburezi mu by'Ubuvuzi.
Ingamba za mbere zatangajwe na leta harimo guhagarika ibitaramo n'indi mihango y'umuco, imikino n'ibirori byo ku wa Gatanu, no gufunga kaminuza, amashuri makuru n'ibigo by'amashuri.
Irani yateganyije miliyari eshanu z'amafaranga y'u Rwanda yo kurwanya virusi.
Perezida Hassan Rouhani yavuze ku wa 26 Gashyantare 2020 ko nta gahunda yo gushyiraho uturere twihariye twibasiwe n'iki cyorezo, ko abantu bonyine ari bo bagombaga kuguma mu kato.
Gahunda yo gushyiraho ingamba zo gutembera mu mijyi yatangajwe muri Werurwe, nubwo urujya n'uruza rwinshi rw'abantu mu mijyi rwagumyeho mbere y'iminsi mikuru y'umwaka mushya w'Ababiligi.
Ahantu hatagatifu ha Shia i Qom hakomeje gufungurirwa abahakanyi kugeza ku ya 16 Werurwe 2020.
Mu gihe havuzwe ko icyorezo cya Iran cyabayeho mu buryo butemewe, ibihugu birenga icumi byakurikiranye abarwayi bacyo bagaruka muri Irani ku itariki ya 28 Gashyantare, bigaragaza ko icyorezo gishobora kuba gikomeye kurusha 388 byatangajwe na leta ya Irani kuri iyo tariki.
Inteko ishinga amategeko ya Irani yahagaritswe, kuko abanyamuryango 23 mu bagize 290 bavugwaho gupima virusi ku ya 3 Werurwe.
Ku ya 12 Werurwe, Umuryango uharanira uburenganzira bwa muntu wahamagariye abayobozi ba gereza za Irani gufungura abarwanashyaka bazira urugomo bazira gukora mu buryo bw'amahoro, no gufungura by'agateganyo imfungwa zose zifite uburenganzira.
Bivugwa ko virusi ifite ibyago byinshi byo kwandura mu bigo byugarijwe nk'amazu y'imbohe, aho usanga hari n'ubutabazi buhagije.
Ku ya 15 Werurwe, leta ya Iran yatangaje ko abantu 100 bapfuye ku munsi, ku rwego rwo hejuru mu gihugu kuva icyorezo cyatangira.
Nibura abantu 12 bicaye cyangwa bahoze ari abanyapolitiki n'abategetsi ba Irani bapfuye bazize iki cyorezo kugeza ku ya 17 Werurwe.
Kugeza ku ya 23 Werurwe, Irani yari imaze kubona abanduye bashya 50 buri saha, ndetse n'uwishwe na coronavirus buri minota 10.
Nk'uko byatangajwe n'abayobozi b'ishami ry'umuryango w'abibumbye ryita ku buzima (OMS), mu gihugu cya Irani, umubare w'abanduye ushobora kuba wikubye inshuro eshanu uw'abamaze kumenyekana.
Yongeyeho ko ibihano bya Amerika kuri Irani bishobora kugira ingaruka ku bushobozi bw'igihugu mu by'imari bwo guhangana n'icyorezo.
Umunyamabanga Mukuru w'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ushinzwe uburenganzira bwa muntu yasabye ko habaho ibihano by'ubukungu ku bihugu byazahajwe n'icyorezo, harimo na Irani.
Icyorezo cyemejwe ko cyakwirakwiriye mu Butaliyani ku ya 31 Mutarama ubwo abashyitsi babiri b'Abashinwa bapimaga ko banduye SARS-CoV-2 i Roma.
Umubare w'abanduye watangiye kwiyongera, bituma leta y'Ubutaliyani ihita ihagarika ingendo zose z'indege ziva cyangwa zijya mu Bushinwa, ndetse itangaza ko igihugu kiri mu bihe by'ubukungu.
Ibibazo bitandukanye by'uburwayi bwa COVID-19 byongeye kugaragara nyuma, bitangirana n'uburwayi 16 muri Lombardy ku ya 21 Gashyantare.Ku ya 22 Gashyantare, Minisiteri y'Ubutegetsi yatangaje amabwiriza mashya yo gukumira icyorezo, harimo no gufunga abantu barenga 50,000 baturutse mu mijyi 11 itandukanye mu majyaruguru y'u Butaliyani.
Minisitiri w'intebe Giuseppe Conte yavuze ko mu turere dufite icyorezo, kwinjira no gusohoka bitazatangwa.
Ku itariki ya 4 Werurwe, leta y'Ubutaliyani yategetse ko amashuri yose na kaminuza bifungwa mu gihugu hose, aho mu gihugu hapfuye abantu bagera ku 100.
Imikino yose ikomeye, harimo n'imikino ya shampiyona ya A, yakomeje kuba nta bareba kugeza muri Mata, ariko ku itariki ya 9 Werurwe imikino yose yahagaritswe by'agateganyo nibura ukwezi.
Ku ya 11 Werurwe, Minisitiri w'Intebe Conte yategetse guhagarika ibikorwa byose by'ubucuruzi uretse amasoko n'amavuriro.Ku ya 6 Werurwe, Ishuri ry'Ubuvuzi mu Butaliyani (SIAARTI) ryatanze amabwiriza ku mahame mbwirizamuco yerekeye ibirori byo guhitamo abarwayi bashobora kuvurwa.
Ku ya 19 Werurwe, Ubutaliyani bwirutse Ubushinwa mu bihugu bifite umubare munini w'abanduye mu isi nyuma y'abantu 3.405 bishwe n'icyorezo.
Ku ya 22 Werurwe, byatangajwe ko Uburusiya bwohereje mu Butaliyani indege icyenda z'intambara zifite ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi.
Kugeza ku ya 5 Mata, mu Butaliyani hari abantu 128,948 bamaze kwandura, 15,887 barapfuye, naho 21,815 bakira, abenshi muri bo bakaba bari mu karere ka Lombardie.
Raporo ya CNN igaragaza ko umubare munini w'abantu bakuze hamwe no kutabona uburyo bwo gupima abanduye kugeza ubu, bishobora kuba ari byo bituma umubare w'abanduye wiyongera.
Igisubizo cy'u Bwongereza kuri virusi cyagaragaye ko ari kimwe mu bihugu by'ingeri zose byahuye n'ingaruka, kandi kugeza ku ya 18 Werurwe 2020, leta y'u Bwongereza ntiyigeze ishyiraho uburyo ubwo ari bwo bwose bwo kwirinda imvururu cyangwa gushyiraho ingamba zo gushyira abantu mu kato ku baturage bayo.
Ku itariki ya 16 Werurwe, Minisitiri w'Intebe Boris Johnson yasohoye itangazo rigira riti "Twirinde ingendo n'imibonano mpuzabitsina bitari ngombwa, kandi dutere abantu inkunga yo gukora mu rugo niba bishoboka, no kwirinda ahantu hatandukanye nko mu tubari, muri resitora no muri za sinema".
Ku ya 20 Werurwe, leta yatangaje ko ahantu hose ho kwidagadurira, nko mu tubari no mu mazu y'imyitozo ngororamubiri, hagomba gufungurwa vuba na bwangu, kandi isezeranya ko izishyura abakozi imishahara igera kuri 80% ku mafaranga 2500 ku kwezi, mu rwego rwo kwirinda ubushomeri mu gihe cy'ikibazo.
Mu buryo butandukanye n'ingamba zabanje, iyi mipaka yashyizweho imbaraga n'abapolisi binyuze mu gutangaza ibihano no guhagarika amateraniro.
"Ubucuruzi bwinshi bwasabwe gufungwa, usibye ubucuruzi bufatwa nk'"ibikenewe"" harimo amasoko, amavuriro, amabanki, amaduka ya mudasobwa, sitasiyo ya lisansi n'ibibuga by'indege".
Ku ya 20 Mutarama, icyorezo cya COVID-19 cya mbere cyemejwe muri leta ya Pacific Northwest ya Washington, cyagaragaye ku mugabo wari watashye avuye muri Wuhan ku ya 15 Mutarama.
Igisirikare cya White House gishinzwe kurwanya Coronavirus cyatangiye ku wa 29 Mutarama.
Ku ya 31 Mutarama, ubuyobozi bwa Trump bwatangaje ko hari ikibazo cy'ubutabazi mu baturage, kandi bushyiraho ingamba zo kwinjira ku bantu baturutse mu Bushinwa.
Ku ya 28 Mutarama 2020, Ikigo gishinzwe kugenzura indwara, ikigo cy'ubutegetsi cya Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika gishinzwe ubuzima rusange, cyatangaje ko cyatangije igikoresho cyo gupima ubwacyo.
Nubwo byari bimeze bityo, Amerika yatangiye vuba mu igerageza, ariko ryahishe aho iki cyorezo cyagaragaye icyo gihe.
Ibizamini byangijwe n'ibikoresho by'ubushakashatsi byakozwe na leta muri Gashyantare, kubura kwemerwa na leta ku bikoresho by'ubushakashatsi bitari ibya leta (n'abaganga, ibigo by'ubucuruzi n'ibitaro) kugeza mu mpera za Gashyantare, no kubahiriza ibisabwa ku bantu bujuje ibisabwa kugira ngo bakore ibizamini kugeza mu ntangiriro za Werurwe (bituma hakenerwa ko abaganga batanga amabwiriza nyuma yaho).
Kugeza ku ya 27 Gashyantare, The Washington Post yatangaje ko hateganyijwe ibizamini bitarenga 4,000 muri Amerika.
Kugeza ku ya 13 Werurwe, ibihugu byo mu nyanja ya Atlantike byari bimaze gutanga raporo y'uko hasi y'ibipimo 14,000 byakozwe.
Ku ya 22 Werurwe, Associated Press yatangaje ko abantu benshi bafite ibimenyetso, kandi ko abaganga bategereje amasaha cyangwa iminsi yo gupima. Nyuma y'urupfu rwa mbere muri Amerika rwavuzwe muri leta ya Washington ku ya 29 Gashyantare, guverineri Jay Inslee yatangaje ko hari ikibazo cy'ubukungu, ndetse n'ibindi bihugu byakurikije ako kanya.
Amashuri yo mu karere ka Seattle yasubitse amasomo ku ya 3 Werurwe, kandi mu kwezi kwa gatatu amashuri yo mu gihugu hose yari afunze. Ku ya 6 Werurwe 2020, Amerika yasabwe gukora igishushanyo mbonera cy'ingaruka za coronavirus nshya mu gihugu, n'itsinda ry'inzobere mu by'indwara z'ibyorezo muri Imperial College London.
Kuri uwo munsi, Perezida Trump yashyize umukono ku itegeko ryo kongera ubushobozi bwo guhangana na coronavirus no kwitegura, riha inkunga agera kuri miliyari 8.3 z'amadolari ya Amerika inzego z'ubutegetsi bw'igihugu mu rwego rwo guhangana n'iki cyorezo.
Amashyirahamwe yashyizeho gahunda yo kubuza abakozi gukora ingendo, guhagarika amateraniro no gushishikariza abakozi gukora mu rugo.
Ibirori byinshi by'imikino n'ibirori by'ibirori by'umwaka byarahagaritswe. Ku ya 11 Werurwe, Trump yatangaje ko yahagaritse ingendo ku bihugu byinshi by'i Burayi, uretse Ubwongereza, mu gihe cy'iminsi 30, mu gihe cy'amezi 13.
Ku munsi wakurikiyeho, yaguye imipaka kugira ngo ikubiyemo u Bwongereza na Irilande.
Ku ya 13 Werurwe, yatangaje ko igihugu cyagize ikibazo cy'ubukungu budasanzwe, bituma amafaranga ya leta ashobora guhangana n'ikibazo.
Guhera ku ya 15 Werurwe, ubucuruzi bwinshi bwafunze cyangwa bugabanya amasaha y'akazi muri Amerika yose mu kugerageza kugabanya ikwirakwira rya virusi.
Kugeza ku ya 17 Werurwe, icyorezo cyari kimaze kwemezwa mu bihugu byose 50 no mu Ntara ya Columbia. Ku ya 23 Werurwe, byatangajwe ko New York City yari ifite abantu 10,700 banduye virusi kurusha Koreya y'Epfo.
Ku ya 25 Werurwe, umuyobozi w'umugi yavuze ko imibare y'abaturage isa n'aho iri kugenda igenda, mu gihe imibare y'abanduye yagabanutseho kabiri, iva ku minsi 2.0 igera ku minsi 4.7.
Ku ya 28 Werurwe, i New York hemejwe ko hari abantu 32,308 banduye, naho 672 bahitanywe na virusi.Ku ya 26 Werurwe, Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika zemejwe ko ari zo zifite umubare munini w'abanduye coronavirus ku isi, zirimo Ubushinwa n'Ubutaliyani.Ku ya 8 Mata, Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika zari zifite abantu 400,335 banduye iyi ndwara, naho abantu 12,841 bakaba barapfuye.
Nk'uko byatangajwe n'ibinyamakuru ku wa 30 Werurwe, Perezida wa Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika, Donald Trump, yafashe icyemezo cyo kongera amabwiriza y'ubufatanye n'abaturage kugeza ku wa 30 Mata.
Kuri uwo munsi, ubwato bwa USNS Comfort, ubwato bw'ibitaro bufite ibitanda bigera ku 1000, bwashyize ikirindiro mu mujyi wa New York.
Ku ya 3 Mata, muri Amerika hapfuye abantu 884 bishwe na coronavirus mu masaha 24.
Muri leta ya New York, abanduye barenga 100,000 ku ya 3 Mata. White House yanenzwe kubera uburyo yitabiriye iterabwoba no gucunga ubutumwa bwatanzwe n'itsinda ry'abaminisitiri b'ubuzima n'abahanga mu by'ubushakashatsi, gutegura ibiganiro bya rubanda n'ibinyamakuru byibanda kuri virusi, hamwe na Visi Perezida Mike Pence.
Kwemera mu buryo bwagutse uburyo Trump yakemuye ikibazo cy'ubukene byananiwe mu nzego z'ubudehe.
Abategetsi ba Amerika n'abavuga rumwe na Leta banenze Amerika kubera ko ishingiye ku byangombwa by'ibanze by'ibanze, harimo n'imiti y'ibanze ituruka mu Bushinwa.
Isesengura ry'ingendo zo mu kirere ryakoreshejwe mu gupima no kureba uburyo ikwirakwira ryagaragaye mu kinyamakuru cy'ubuvuzi cy'ingendo cyo hagati muri Mutarama 2020.
Hashingiwe ku makuru yo mu mwaka wa 2018 yatanzwe n'ishyirahamwe mpuzamahanga ry'ingendo z'indege, Bangkok, Hong Kong, Tokyo na Taipei ni byo bihugu bifite umubare munini w'abagenzi baturutse i Wuhan.
Dubai, Sydney na Melbourne na byo byavuzwe ko ari byo bihugu bikunzwe cyane ku bantu baturuka i Wuhan.
Ibirwa bya Bali byavuzwe ko ari byo bifite ubushobozi buke mu mijyi 20 y'ibihe by'ibanze mu bijyanye no kwitegura, mu gihe imijyi yo muri Ositaraliya yabonetse ko ari yo ifite ubushobozi bwinshi.
Iryo tangazo rivuga ko abenshi mu bantu banduye COVID-19 bataraboneka, kandi ko Australia izashyira imbaraga mu gucunga imipaka no guhuza abantu mu gisubizo cyayo cy'icyorezo.
Ku itariki ya 21 Werurwe, mu gihugu cya Ositaraliya hatangajwe ko habayeho ikibazo cy'ubukungu bw'umuntu.
Mu kwerekana uburyo bw'ikoranabuhanga mu gutwara abantu i Wuhan na Hubei, ibihugu byinshi byateguye kwimura abaturage babyo n'abakozi ba ambasade mu karere, cyane cyane binyuze mu ndege z'ibihugu bikorera ku butaka, mu gihe abategetsi b'Ubushinwa babisabye.
Canada, Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika, Ubuyapani, Ubuhinde, Shire, Australia, Ubufaransa, Argentine, Arumeniya na Tayilande ni bimwe mu bihugu bya mbere byatangiye gahunda yo kwimura abaturage babyo.
Pakisitani yavuze ko itazongera guhungisha abaturage bayo mu Bushinwa.
Ku ya 7 Gashyantare, Brezil yakuye abaturage 34 b'Abanyamerika cyangwa imiryango yabo, hiyongeraho Abanyapolonye bane, Umunyashinwa umwe n'Umuhindi umwe.
Abaturage bo muri Polonye, Ubushinwa n'Ubuhinde bavuye mu ndege muri Polonye aho indege ya Brazil yari ihagarariye mbere yo kujya muri Brezili.
Abaturage ba Brazil bari bagiye i Wuhan bashyizwe mu kato ku kigo cya gisirikare hafi y'umujyi wa Brasília.
Kuri uwo munsi, Abanyakanada 215 (176 bavuye mu ndege ya mbere na 39 bavuye mu ndege ya kabiri yateguwe na leta ya Amerika) bakuwe i Wuhan bajya ku kigo cya CFB Trento kugira ngo bajye mu kato k'ibyumweru bibiri.
Ku ya 11 Gashyantare, indi ndege yari itwaye Abakanada 185 ivuye i Wuhan yageze ku kigo cy'ingabo cya CFB Trenton.
Abategetsi ba Australia bakuye abantu 277 ku itariki ya 3 n'iya 4 z'ukwezi kwa kabiri, babajyana mu kigo cya gereza cya Christmas Island, aho bazajya bafungirwa mu gihe cy'iminsi 14.
Abari muri iyo ndege (harimo n'abari baturutse muri Australia na Pacific) bashyizwe mu kato ku kigo cya gisirikare cya gisirikare cya gisirikare mu mujyi wa Whangaparoa, mu majyaruguru ya Auckland.
Ku ya 15 Gashyantare, Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika zatangaje ko zizakora igikorwa cyo guhungisha Abanyamerika bari mu bwato bwa Diamond Princess.
Ku ya 21 Gashyantare, indege yari itwaye Abakanada 129 bari bahawe ubuhungiro mu bwato bwa Diamond Princess bwari bwarahagaze i Trenton, Ontario.
Mu ntangiriro z'ukwezi kwa gatatu, leta y'Ubuhinde yatangiye guhungisha abaturage bayo muri Irani. Ku itariki ya 14 Werurwe, indege y'indege y'indege ya South African Airways ikoreshwa na leta ya Afurika y'Epfo, yahungishije abaturage 112 bo muri Afurika y'Epfo.
Ibizamini by'ubuzima byakozwe mbere yo kugenda, kandi Abanyafurika b'Epfo bane bagaragazaga ibimenyetso bya coronavirus barasiwe kugira ngo bagabanye ibyago.
Gusa abanyafurika y'Epfo bagaragaje ko batitabye Imana ni bo bonyine bakorewe ikizamini cy'ubwoko.
Ibyavuye mu igerageza byasuzuguye abanyafurika y'Epfo bose, harimo abapilote, abakozi bo mu ndege, abapolisi n'abasirikare bari mu butumwa bw'ubutabazi, bose bagumye mu kato kandi batarabarurwa mu gihe cy'iminsi 14 mu kigo cya Vrasil.
Ku ya 20 Werurwe, Amerika yatangiye gukura ingabo zayo muri Iraq kubera ikwirakwira ry'icyorezo.
Ku ya 5 Gashyantare, Minisiteri y'Ububanyi n'Amahanga y'u Bushinwa yemeje ko ibihugu 21 (harimo Belarusi, Uburusiya, Pakisitani, Trinité na Tobago, Misiri na Irani) byoherereje imfashanyo u Bushinwa.
Abanyeshuri b'Abashinwa bo muri kaminuza zo muri Amerika bifatanyije mu gufasha kohereza imfashanyo mu bice by'u Bushinwa byibasiwe na virusi, aho itsinda ry'abakozi b'ubutabazi mu karere ka Chicago batangaje ko batanze udupfukamunwa 50,000 tw'ubwoko bwa N95 ku bitaro byo mu ntara ya Hubei ku wa 30 Mutarama.
Ku ya 5 Gashyantare, Bill na Melinda Gates batangaje ko batanze miliyoni 100 z'amadolari y'Amerika mu rwego rwo gushyigikira ubushakashatsi ku nkingo n'imiti, ndetse no kurinda abaturage bafite ibyago muri Afurika no muri Aziya y'Epfo.
Ikigo Interaksyon cyatangaje ko guverinoma y'Ubushinwa yatanze udupfukamunwa 200,000 muri Philippines ku ya 6 Gashyantare, nyuma y'aho Senateri Richard Gordon yohereje udupfukamunwa miliyoni 3.16 mu mujyi wa Wuhan.
Ku ya 19 Gashyantare, Karayibe itukura ya Singapore yatangaje ko igiye kohereza inkunga ya miliyoni 2.26 z'amadolari y'u Bushinwa.
Ubuyapani bwatanze udupfukamunwa miliyoni imwe mu karere ka Wuhan, Turukiya yohereje ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi mu buryo bwihuse, Uburusiya bwohereje toni 13 z'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi mu karere ka Wuhan, Maleziya yatangaje ko yatanze udupfukamunwa miliyoni 18 mu Bushinwa, Ubudage bwohereje ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi birimo udupfukamunwa 10,000, Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika zatanze ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi 17.8 z'amadolari y'amanyamerika, ndetse zitanga n'andi mafaranga miliyoni 100 y'amazi yo gufasha abafite ubwandu mu gihugu cya China nyuma yo koherezwa mu Bushinwa.
Muri Werurwe, Ubushinwa, Cuba n'Uburusiya byohereje ibikoresho n'abahanga mu by'ubuvuzi gufasha Ubutaliyani guhangana n'icyorezo cya coronavirus.
Umucuruzi Jack Ma yohereje ibikoresho by'ipimisha bya miliyoni 1.1, udupfukamunwa miliyoni 6 n'udupfukamunwa 60.000 mu mujyi wa Addis Ababa muri Ethiopia, kugira ngo bitangirwe Umuryango wa Afurika Yunze Ubumwe.
Nyuma yaho, yohereje ibikoresho 5,000 by'igerageza, udupfukamunwa 100,000 n'ibikoresho bitanu by'umwuka muri Panama.
MA kandi yatanze ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi muri Canada. Ubuholandi, Esipanye, Turukiya, Kazakisitani na Repubulika ya Chechnya byatangaje impungenge ku masike n'ibikoresho byo gupima byakozwe n'Abashinwa.
Urugero, Esipanye yakuyeho ibikoresho 58,000 by'ubushinwa by'ipima coronavirus, byerekana 30% gusa, mu gihe Ubuholandi bwasubijeho udupfukamunwa 600,000 tw'Ubushinwa tw'igihombo.
U Bubiligi bwakusanyije udupfukamunwa 100,000 tutari twungurujwe, twibukwa ko twavuye mu Bushinwa ariko mu by'ukuri twavuye muri Colombia.
Ku rundi ruhande, imfashanyo y'u Bushinwa yakiriwe neza mu bice bimwe na bimwe bya Amerika y'Epfo na Afurika. Ku itariki ya 2 y'ukwezi kwa gatanu, Banki y'Isi yatangije igikorwa cy'ubutabazi bw'ubutabazi mu bihugu bikiri mu nzira y'amajyambere.
Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) ryashimiye abayobozi b'u Bushinwa ku bw'imihati bashyizeho mu kurwanya iki cyorezo.
Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) ryagaragaje itandukaniro hagati y'icyorezo cya SARS cyabaye mu mwaka wa 2002-2004, aho abategetsi b'u Bushinwa bashinjwaga guhisha ibanga ryatumaga batabasha gukumira no kugenzura uko ibintu byifashe, n'icyorezo cy'ubu, aho leta y'u Bushinwa yatanze amakuru buri gihe kugira ngo hatagira urujijo mbere y'umunsi mukuru w'ubushyinguro.
Ku ya 23 Mutarama, mu gusubiza icyemezo cy'ubuyobozi bw'igihugu cyo gushyiraho gahunda yo guhagarika ingendo i Wuhan, uhagarariye OMS Gauden Galea yavuze ko nubwo atari inama yatanzwe na OMS, ari icyemezo gikomeye cyo kwibanda ku kurwanya icyorezo aho cyibasiwe cyane, avuga ko ari icyorezo kitigeze kibaho mu mateka y'ubuzima rusange.Ku ya 30 Mutarama, nyuma yo kwemeza ko cyanduye abantu batari Abashinwa, n'ubwiyongere bw'abanduye mu bindi bihugu, perezida w'igihugu cy'u Bushinwa yatangaje ko icyorezo cyibasiye ibihugu bitandukanye, kuva mu nama ya mbere y'umuryango mpuzamahanga wita ku buzima (OMS) yo mu 2009, ari kimwe mu byatangajwe ko ari icyorezo cyibasiye Isi.
Umuyobozi Mukuru wa OMS, Tedros Adhanom, yavuze ko PHEIC ari kubera ibyago byo gukwirakwira ku isi hose, cyane cyane mu bihugu bifite umushahara muto n'uhagati, bidakoresha uburyo bwiza bwo kwivuza.
Mu gusubiza ku bijyanye no gushyiraho ingamba zo gukumira ingendo, Tedros yavuze ko "nta mpamvu yo gushyiraho ingamba zo kubangamira ingendo n'ubucuruzi mpuzamahanga bitari ngombwa" kandi ko "Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima ritagombye gushyiraho ingamba zo gukumira ingendo n'ubucuruzi".
"Ku ya 5 Gashyantare, Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) ryasabye umuryango mpuzamahanga gutanga miliyoni 675 z'amadolari yo gushyigikira ibikorwa by'ubwiteganyirize mu bihugu bikennye, rivuga ko byihutirwa gushyigikira ibihugu bitagira uburyo bwo gushakisha abantu banduye virusi nubwo yaba yongeye kuboneka".
"Tedros yakomeje avuga ko ""ibihugu byose, iyo hari umuntu umwe ufite intege nke, ari kimwe n'abandi bose bafite intege nke"" kandi asaba umuryango mpuzamahanga ""kushora imari uyu munsi, ntabwo bizatwara igihe kinini nyuma"" Mu kiganiro n'abanyamakuru cyo ku wa 11 Gashyantare, Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima ryise icyorezo COVID-19".
Kuri uwo munsi, Tedros yemeje ko umunyamabanga mukuru wa ONU António Guterres yemeye guha ububasha umuryango wose wa ONU mu gusubiza.
"Itsinda ry'umuryango w'abibumbye ryita ku bibazo ryashyizweho, rituma habaho guhuza ibisubizo by'umuryango w'abibumbye, aho OMS izatuma ikomeza kwibanda ku bisubizo by'ubuzima, mu gihe izindi nzego zishobora kuzana ubuhanga bwazo mu gufasha mu iterambere ry'ubukungu n'imibereho myiza y'abantu n'ingaruka z'icyorezo""".
Ku ya 14 Gashyantare, itsinda ry'abakozi b'ubumisiyonari ba WHO hamwe n'u Bushinwa ryashinzwe kugira ngo rihe impuguke mpuzamahanga na WHO amakuru yihutirwa mu Bushinwa, kugira ngo bafashe mu gucunga ubukana bw'icyorezo mu karere no gupima ubukana n'ubushobozi bwo kwanduza icyorezo, hashyirwaho amahugurwa n'inama n'ibigo by'ingenzi by'igihugu, no gukora ingendo zimbitse zo gusobanukirwa ingaruka z'ingamba zo gusubiza mu ntara n'uturere, harimo n'imidugudu n'imidugudu. Ku ya 25 Gashyantare, OMS yatangaje ko isi igomba gufata ingamba nyinshi zo kwitegura icyorezo cya Coronavirus, ivuga ko mu gihe cy'icyorezo cy'icyorezo, ibihugu byose byagombye kwitegura.
Mu gusubiza ikwirakwira ry'icyorezo muri Irani, Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima ryoherejeyo itsinda ry'abakozi ba ONU mu rwego rwo gupima uko ibintu byifashe.Ku wa 28 Gashyantare, umukozi wa OMS yavuze ko igipimo cy'ibyago bya coronavirus ku rwego rw'isi kizazamurwa kiva kuri "cyakomeye cyane", ari na cyo kigero cyo hejuru cyo kwitonda no gusuzuma.
Mike Ryan, umuyobozi wa gahunda z'ubutabazi za WHO, yibukije mu itangazo ko "ibi ari ibigeragezo kuri buri leta yo ku isi: nimukanguke".
"Virusi ishobora kuba iri mu nzira, bityo rero ugomba "kwitegura" ushishikariye ko uburyo bwiza bwo gusubiza bushobora gufasha isi kwirinda" ingaruka mbi cyane. "
Ryan yakomeje avuga ko amakuru ariho ubu atemezwa ku buryo abayobozi b'ubuzima bw'abaturage bashobora gutangaza icyorezo ku isi, avuga ko gutangaza bene ako kageni bizaba bisobanura ko "twemera ko buri muntu wese ku isi azandura virusi".
Ku itariki ya 11 Werurwe, Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima ryatangaje ko hagiye kubaho icyorezo cya Coronavirus.
Umuyobozi Mukuru yavuze ko OMS ifite impungenge zikomeye kubera urwego rw'icyorezo cyugarije isi n'uburemere bwacyo ndetse no kutagira ingamba zihamye. OMS yanenzwe cyane kubera ko nta muti uhagije wabonetse kuri iki cyorezo, harimo gutangaza byihuse ko ari ikibazo cy'ubutabazi mu buzima rusange no gushyiraho icyorezo.
Igisubizo cy'icyo kibazo cyabaye itegeko ryo gusaba Tedros Adhanom, umuyobozi mukuru wa OMS, kwegura, ryashyizweho umukono n'abantu 733.000 kugeza ku itariki ya 6 Mata.
