Gukaraba intoki n'isabune ku bihe by'ingenzi by'umunsi birinda ikwirakwira ry'indwara zitandukanye, urugero nk'indwara z'ibicurane n'izindi ndwara zandurira mu kanwa.
Abantu bashobora kandi kwandura indwara z'ubuhumekero, urugero nk'ibicurane cyangwa ibicurane bisanzwe, urugero, iyo badakarabye intoki mbere yo gukora ku maso yabo, ku mazuru cyangwa ku munwa (urugero, iyo batangiye gukorora).
Ibintu bitanu by'ingenzi buri munsi bigomba gukoreshwa mu gukaraba intoki n'isabune birimo mbere na nyuma yo gukaraba, nyuma yo gukaraba umwana, cyangwa guhindurira umwana urwobo, mbere yo gushyiraho ibyokurya, mbere yo kurya, mbere cyangwa nyuma yo gutegura amafunguro, cyangwa guteka inyama, amafi n'inyoni.
Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima ryatanze inama yo gukaraba intoki: Dushobora gukaraba intoki dukoresheje umufuka w'amazi cyangwa isabune.
Mbere yo guteka, mu gihe cyo guteka, na nyuma yo guteka.
Mbere na nyuma yo kwita ku murwayi.
Nyuma yo guhindura impapuro z'ibanze z'umwana cyangwa gukaraba umwana wakoresheje ubwiherero.
Nyuma yo gukaraba mu mazuru cyangwa mu mazuru.
Nyuma yo gukora ku matungo, ku byatsi byayo cyangwa ku bintu byayo byasigaye.
Gucisha mu maboko mu buryo bw'umwuka byibanda ku gukora imyitozo ngororamubiri ijyanye n'uburyo bwo kwigisha bw'umwarimu.
Gukaraba intoki mbere yo gufata imiti cyangwa kuvurwa bishobora gukumira cyangwa kugabanya ikwirakwira ry'indwara.
Intego nyamukuru yo gukaraba intoki ni ukudahumana intoki ziterwa n'ibikoresho byandura (bakteriya, virusi cyangwa ibindi binyabuzima byangiza bishobora gutera indwara) n'ibikoresho bya kirimbuzi bishobora guteza akaga cyangwa indwara.
Ni ingenzi cyane ku bantu bigenga ku biribwa cyangwa mu buvuzi, ariko ni ingenzi no ku baturage muri rusange.
Gukaraba intoki bifite akamaro kanini ku buzima, harimo kugabanya ikwirakwira ry'indwara z'ibicurane, coronavirusi n'izindi ndwara zandura; gukumira indwara z'ibicurane, kugabanya ubwandu bw'ubuhumekero.
no kugabanya umubare w'abana bapfa mu gihe cyo kubyarira mu rugo.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mu mwaka wa 2013 bwagaragaje ko gukaraba intoki bishobora gutuma abana bari munsi y'imyaka itanu bagira amajyambere make.
Mu bihugu bikiri mu nzira y'amajyambere, impfu z'abana ziterwa n'indwara z'ubuhumekero n'indwara z'ibihaha zishobora kugabanuka binyuze mu gushyiraho ingamba zoroshye zo guhindura imyitwarire, nko gukaraba intoki n'isabune.
Iyi mikorere yoroshye ishobora kugabanya umubare w'abapfa bazize izi ndwara ku kigero cya 50%.
Ubuvugizi bushyigikira gukaraba intoki bushobora kugabanya indwara ya kanseri ku kigero cya kimwe cya gatatu, kandi ibyo birashobora kugereranywa no gutanga amazi meza mu duce dufite amikoro make.
48% by'ibikoresho bigabanya indwara z'ibicurane bishobora guhuzwa no gukaraba intoki n'isabune. Gukaraba intoki n'isabune ni bumwe mu buryo bw'ingirakamaro kandi buhendutse bwo kwirinda indwara z'ibicurane n'ubwandu bw'ubwandu bw'ubuhumekero (ARI), kandi ni umuco ukwiriye gukoreshwa mu bigo, amashuri n'imiryango ku isi hose.
Indwara y'ibicurane, ari yo ARI ikomeye, ni yo mpamvu ya mbere y'urupfu mu bana bari munsi y'imyaka itanu, yica abana bagera kuri miliyoni 1.8 buri mwaka.
Indwara ya kanseri n'indwara y'ibihaha bihitana abana bagera kuri miliyoni 3.5 buri mwaka.
Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku buzima (UNICEF) rivuga ko gukaraba intoki n'isabune mbere yo kurya na nyuma yo gukaraba ari byo bishobora kurokora ubuzima kurusha inkingo cyangwa ubundi buryo ubwo ari bwo bwose bwo kuvura, mu kugabanya urupfu rw'indwara ya kanseri hafi icya kabiri, n'urupfu rw'indwara z'ubuhumekero ku kigero cya kane.
Gukaraba intoki ubusanzwe bijyanirana n'ibindi bikorwa by'isuku, bikaba ari bimwe mu bigize gahunda y'amazi, isuku n'isuku.
Gukaraba intoki bishobora no kurinda indwara z'uruhu zanduzwa no guhanahana intoki.
Kimwe mu ngaruka mbi z'ukubanza ni uko gukaraba intoki kenshi bishobora kwangiza uruhu kubera ko rwuma.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe n'u Danemark mu mwaka wa 2012 bwerekanye ko gukaraba intoki cyane bishobora gutera imitsi y'uruhu izwi nka "hand-sore" cyangwa "hand-squamation", cyane cyane mu bakozi b'ubuzima.
Gukaraba intoki kenshi na byo birafatwa nk'ikimenyetso cy'uburwayi bwo mu mutwe.
Ibihe bitanu by'ingenzi ku munsi ugomba gukaraba intoki n'isabune ni ugugabanya ubwandu bw'ubwonko n'umunwa: nyuma yo kujya mu bwiherero (gukaraba intoki nto n'iz'amaboko manini), nyuma yo gukaraba abana (guhindura icyayi cy'umwana), mbere yo guha umwana ibyo kurya, nyuma yo kurya, na mbere cyangwa nyuma yo gutegura ibiryo cyangwa guteka, cyangwa gukaraba amafi cyangwa inyoni.
Ubundi buryo bwo gukaraba intoki bukwiye, ni ukubikora mbere na nyuma yo kuvura igikomere cyangwa inkoni; nyuma yo gukorora, gukorora cyangwa gukorora intoki zawe; nyuma yo gukora ku bintu by'inyamaswa cyangwa ku bikoko; na nyuma yo gukora ku myanda.
Mu bihugu byinshi, umubare w'abantu bakoresha isabune mu ntoki uracyari hasi.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mu mwaka wa 2015 ku isuku y'amaboko bwakorewe mu bihugu 54 bwerekanye ko ku bantu bari mu rugo ku kigereranyo cya 38.7% bakoreshaga isabune mu gukaraba intoki. Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mu mwaka wa 2014 bwagaragaje ko Arabiya Sawudite ari yo ifite igipimo cyo hejuru cyane ari 97% , Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika ni 77% , naho Ubushinwa ni 23% gusa.
Porogaramu y'ubwisungane mu kwivuza ikorwa n'ishami ry'uburezi muri Filipine ni urugero rw'ibikorwa by'ubushake mu guteza imbere ubuzima n'uburezi bw'abana.
Gukuramo udukoko kabiri mu mwaka, hamwe no gukaraba intoki buri munsi n'isabune yo gukaraba amenyo buri munsi hamwe na fluorite, ni intambwe y'ingenzi muri gahunda y'igihugu.
Nanone kandi, byakozwe neza muri Indoneziya.
Gukata amenyo mu buryo bworoshye, ni ukwisukura ukoresheje isabune cyangwa isabune mu mazi.
Ibikorwa by'ibanze by'isabune n'imiti yica udukoko ni ukugabanya inzitizi z'isukari no kongera ubwonko.
Amazi yonyine si uburyo bwiza bwo gusukura uruhu, kuko ibinure na poroteyine, ari byo bigize umubiri w'ibinyabuzima byo mu butaka, bidashobora kuboneka mu mazi.
Ariko kandi, amazi ashyushye ashobora gufasha mu kumesa.
Kubera ko isabune ikomeye, dushobora kuyisubiramo, irimo za bagiteri, imyanda n'isabune nyuma yo kuyikoresha rimwe.
Ubushakashatsi buto bwagenzuye imikorere y'ibinyabutabire byaturutse mu isabune y'umunyu, bwagaragaje ko imikorere y'ibinyabutabire bisa n'aho idashobora guhinduka kuko byamaze gukurwaho n'ibinyabutabire.
"CDC iracyakomeza kuvuga ngo "" amazi y'isabune mu isahani ifite umutwe w'inkomamashyi ni yo meza cyane. ""
Bavuga cyane ku byerekeye isabune n'ibikoresho by'ubumara bifasha abantu kwirinda indwara.
Kugeza ubu, nta bimenyetso bifatika byerekana ko gukoresha umuti wa antibiotique cyangwa umuti wa bactericidal ari byo byonyine byemeza ko umubiri urwanya imiti ya antibiotique mu buryo butandukanye.
Nyamara, isabune yo gukingira bakayire irimo imiti isanzwe yo kurwanya bakayire nka trichlose, ifite ubushobozi bwo kurinda ibiro byinshi by'umubiri.
Niba rero batatoranyije udukoko duto cyane tubasha kurwanya izo ndwara, nta kintu na kimwe cyafasha nk'uko bigaragazwa.
Uretse intungamubiri, kwirinda imikorere y'umubiri n'ibikoresho byo kurinda uruhu, ubu buryo bw'ibishyimbo bufite intungamubiri za acetic acid, asidi ya esophagic, asiatique, PH, umuti wica udukoko n'uburozi bwo kurinda uruhu (urugero: umutobe w'ibishyimbo, vitamini mantoli n'ibikomoka ku bidukikije). Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe na Kaminuza ya Oregon School of Public Health bwagaragaje ko isabune isanzwe ari nziza nko nk'isabuni yica udukoko irimo trichlosan mu kwirinda indwara n'ubwandu bw'uruhu.
Amazi ashyushye cyane yo gukaraba intoki ntabwo ashyushye bihagije kugira ngo yice mikorobe.
Iyo mikorobe ikura vuba cyane ku bushyuhe bw'umubiri (°37 C).
Ariko kandi, amazi ashyushye, isabune ni ingirakamaro kurusha amazi akonje n'isabune mu gusukura amavuta y'ibanze, ubutaka n'udukoko.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe n'abahanga, butandukanye n'uko abantu benshi babyemera, bwagaragaje ko gukoresha amazi ashyushye bidakemura ibibazo by'imirire mibi iri ku kiganza.
Amazi yo gukaraba intoki cyangwa se umuti wo kugabanya ubukana bw'intoki ni imiti yo gukaraba intoki idakoresha amazi.
Mu mpera z'imyaka ya za 1990 no mu ntangiriro z'ikinyejana cya 21, ibikoresho byo gukaraba intoki bitagira amazi, urugero nka alcohol (byitwa alcohol wash, hand wash, hand sanitizer, hand wash) byatangiye gukundwa cyane.
Byinshi bishingiye kuri isobutroline cyangwa ethanol, hamwe na sosi itandukanye nka carburant (ibikoresho bya polyester bya acrylic acid) mu gels cyangwa ibindi bikoresho nka glycerin mu bikoresho by'amazi cyangwa imyungu kugirango byorohereze gukoresha no kugabanya imbaraga zo gukama kwa alkali.
Kongeraho ikinyabutabire cya hydrogen-peroxide byongera ibikorwa byo kwica udukoko. Amazi yo gukaraba afite nibura 60 kugeza kuri 95% by'umwuka wa alkaline ni yo yica udukoko
Amazi yo gukaraba asenya mikorobe isanzwe, mikorobe zidakira imiti (MRSA na VRE), indwara z'ibicurane na virusi zimwe na zimwe (harimo SIDA, virusi ya SARS, virusi ya RSV, virusi y'ibicurane, urukingo rwa tuberculose n'indwara y'ibicurane) n'imiti.
Amazi yo gukaraba arimo inzoga 70% yica 99,97%, igabanya3,5 (ni ukuvuga 35 decibels) y'ubwandu bw'udukoko ku ntoki nyuma y'amasegonda 30 yakoreshejwe, na 99,99% kugeza kuri 99,999% (igabanya 4 kugeza kuri 5 logs) y'ubwandu bw'udukoko ku ntoki nyuma y'umunota umwe. Amazi yo gukaraba akoresha inzoga ni yo ikora cyane ku mikorobe, kandi ni make cyane ku mikorobe imwe n'imwe.
Amazi yo gukaraba intoki arimo inzoga nta ngaruka agira ku ndwara ya norovirus (cyangwa Norwalk), ari na yo mpamvu ikunze gutera indwara ya paratire. Gukaraba intoki cyangwa gusukura intoki mu buryo buhagije hakoreshwa inzoga cyangwa se gufunga intoki ku mpande zose.
Inkoramutima, intoki zombi n'ibiganza byose by'intoki byombi byashyizwe mu mazi mu gihe cy'amasegonda 30 kugeza igihe ikintu cy'umwimerere kibaye ikinyampeke cyangwa cyumye.
Ikigo cy'Amerika gishinzwe kurwanya indwara (CDC) cyasabye ko umuntu yakwihana indwara akoresheje amazi, cyane cyane iyo ari intoki zanduye.
Ikigaragara ni uko ikoreshwa ry'izo nkingo ryongerewe bitewe n'uko zikoreshwa mu buryo bworoshye kandi zikora vuba mu kurwanya indwara z'uruhu. Ariko kandi, ntizikwiye gusimbura gukaraba intoki neza, keretse gusa iyo nta sabuni n'amazi bihari.
Gukoresha ibikoresho byo gukaraba intoki bikuraho udukoko duhumanya umubiri akenshi bishobora gutuma uruhu rukuma, keretse hagize ikintu cyongera imyanda y'uruhu n'/cyangwa imyuka y'uruhu mu mubiri.
Ingaruka zo gukama za alcohol zishobora kugabanuka cyangwa kuzimanganywa hiyongereyeho amavuta ya glycerine na/cyangwa ibindi bintu byongera uruhu mu buryo bw'imiterere.
Mu igerageza ry'ubuvuzi, gukaraba intoki bifite intungamubiri zituma uruhu ruba rufite ibisebe bike kandi rukagira uruhu rwumutse kurusha isabune cyangwa isabune yica udukoko.
Kuribwa kw'uruhu biturutse ku kintu cyanduza, ibimenyetso by'indwara y'ubuhumekero, inzoga nyinshi cyangwa inzoga cyangwa ibindi bintu by'ibanze biri mu bikoresho byo gukaraba intoki, ni ibintu bidakunze kubaho.
Gusuzuma gake bishobora gutera indwara z'uruhu ziterwa no guhura n'imihindagurikire y'imikorere y'uruhu, byagiye biba ikintu gishishikaje cyane ugereranyije no gukaraba intoki n'isabune n'amazi.
Uretse kuba ari ingirakamaro, imiti itarimo amazi ntishobora gukaraba intoki zirimo mikorobe, ariko ishobora kwica mikorobe mu buryo bworoshye.
Kubera iyo mpamvu, gukaraba intoki ntibigira ingaruka nk'iz'isabune n'amazi mu gukumira ikwirakwira ry'imitsi mibi myinshi ishobora gutera indwara, kuko imiti iteza indwara ikomeza kuba ku ntoki.
Ubushobozi bw'amazi yo gukaraba adafite inzoga bushingiye cyane ku bikoresho n'uburyo bwo gukaraba, kandi mu mateka, amazi y'inzoga n'amazi yo gukaraba amaboko ntibyabaga bifite akamaro.
Vuba aha, amavuta akoresha benzalkonium yagaragajwe ko agira ubukana kandi ko agira ubukana bwiyongereye nyuma yo gukoresha, bitandukanye na alkol, yagaragajwe ko igira ubukana buke nyuma yo gukoresha inshuro nyinshi, birashoboka ko biterwa n'uko igisubizo cy'uruhu kiza ku kigero cyo hejuru.
Abantu benshi bo mu baturage bafite amikoro make ntibashobora kubona isabune cyangwa ngo bakoreshe ubutaka.
Gukaraba ku nkono cyangwa hasi bishobora kuba byiza kurusha gukaraba amazi gusa, ariko si ko bimeze nko gukaraba isabune.
Hari impungenge ko iyo ubutaka cyangwa ibyatsi byanduye mikorobe, bishobora kongera ikwirakwira ry'indwara aho kuyigabanya.
Umutobe ni umuti wica mikorobe nk'isabune, kuko iyo uhuye n'amazi, utanga umuti wa alkaline.
Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima ryasabye ko mu gihe nta sabuni ihari hakoreshwa isahani cyangwa umusenyi.
Uburyo bwiza bwo gukaraba intoki, bwasabwe n'Ikigo cy'Amerika gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara, mu kwirinda kwandura indwara zikurikira:
Jya ukaraba intoki ukoresheje amazi ashyushye cyangwa akonje.
Bagira inama yo gukoresha amazi ashyushye kuko amazi yo mu mazi ashobora kuba ari menshi, kandi ubushyuhe bwo mu mazi nta tandukaniro busa n'aho bufite.
Gushyira isabune mu biganza, kubisukisha amenyo menshi y'isabune, harimo ijosi, hagati y'intoki n'amavi.
Isabuni ishobora gukuraho mikorobe mu ruhu, kandi ubushakashatsi bwagaragaje ko abantu benshi bakunda gukaraba intoki neza bakoresheje isabune aho gukaraba amazi.
Gushyiraho nibura amasegonda 20.
Gukaraba bituma habaho imikorere mibi, kandi gukaraba igihe kirekire kurushaho bishobora gutuma habaho imikorere mibi cyane.
Jya ukaraba neza munsi y'amazi atemba.
Gukaraba mu kintu cyo kwiyuhagiramo (cyangwa se kitarimo amazi) bishobora gutuma intoki zawe zongera kwandura.
Fata igitambaro gitunganye maze ukarabe intoki cyangwa ureke bikome mu muyaga.
Ibiganza byanduye n'ibiganza byanduye birashobora kongera kwandura. Ahantu hakunze gukomereka ni mu biganza, mu ntoki, hagati y'intoki no munsi y'urutoki.
Imyungu n'imiti yo kugabanya imyuzure bishobora kuba ahantu hatuma habaho udukoko duto duto mu mubiri.
Gukaraba intoki mu buryo buteye isoni ni byo bikunze gukoreshwa kugira ngo intoki zidakomoka.
Amahitamo menshi y'ibanze ashobora gukorwa kugira ngo byorohereze gukaraba intoki ahantu hadashyizwemo amazi n'isabune, urugero: kuvoma amazi mu bigega cyangwa mu byuma bifite imiterere ikwiriye, kandi/cyangwa gukoresha imashini iyo bibaye ngombwa mu bihugu bikiri mu nzira y'amajyambere. Mu mimerere aho amazi atangwa ari make (nk'amashuri cyangwa uturere tw'icyaro mu bihugu bikiri mu nzira y'amajyambere), hari ibisubizo byo kubungabunga amazi nka "tippy-taps" n'andi mahitamo y'ibanze.
Igikoresho cyo kuvoma amazi ni ikoranabuhanga risanzwe rikoresha igikoresho cy'amazi gihingwa n'umugozi, ukoresheje ikirenge kugira ngo ushyire amazi make ku ntoki zawe hamwe n'isabune.
Kumesa neza intoki ni igice cy'ingenzi mu gikorwa cyo gukaraba intoki, ariko hari impaka zimwe na zimwe ku buryo bwo kumesa neza mu byumba bya rusange.
Ubushakashatsi bugenda bwiyongera bugaragaza ko impapuro z'isuku ari zo zanduza cyane kuruta imashini zimesa intoki ziri mu byumba byinshi by'ubwiherero.
Mu mwaka wa 2008, ubushakashatsi bwakozwe n'ikigo cy'ubushakashatsi cya kaminuza ya Westminster, mu mujyi wa Londres, ndetse n'ikigo cy'ubucuruzi bw'imyanda cyitwa European Tissue Symposium, bwagereranyije imyanda ituruka ku myenda n'ibindi bikoresho by'imyanda bikoreshwa mu gihe cya none.
Nyuma yo gukaraba no gukaraba intoki hakoreshejwe ikuma ikongerera imyanda, habonetse ubwiyongere bw'ibinyabutabire ku bikoresho byo mu ntoki, ku kigero cya 194% no ku rutoki ku kigero cya 254%.
Kumesa n'umushongi byateje ubwiyongere bw'umubare w'udukoko ku munwa ku kigero cya 42% no ku rutoki ku kigero cya 15%.
Nyuma yo gukaraba no gukaraba intoki ukoresheje umwanda, umubare w'udukoko duto duto wagabanyutse ku kigero cya 76% ku bikoresho byo gukaraba no ku biganza ku kigero cya 77%. Abahanga mu bya siyansi bakoze kandi ibizamini kugira ngo bamenye niba hari ibyago byo kwanduza abantu bakoresha akumba k'ubwiherero n'ahandi hose mu bwiherero, bitewe n'uburyo bwo gukama buri wese.
Imashini ikama, ituma umuyaga uva mu cyuma ku muvuduko wa 180 m/s (650 km/h 400 mph), ishobora kwirukana mikorobe mu ntoki no mu gikoresho gikama, kandi ishobora guhuma abandi bakoresha icyumba cy'ubwiherero n'aho bakirira mu birometero bibiri.
Gukoresha imashini yo kumesa bishobora gukwirakwiza imyanda (ibinyabuzima bito) kugeza kuri metero 0.25 uvuye mu gikoresho cyo kumesa.
Uruhu rw'uburozi ntirugaragariza imikorere ya mikorobe. Mu mwaka wa 2005, ubushakashatsi bwakozwe na TÜV Produkt und Umwel bwakoze igenzura ku buryo butandukanye bwo kumesa intoki.
Gukurikirana impinduka mu mibare ya bakteraya nyuma yo gukata intoki byabonetse bikurikira:
Hashize igihe kinini, habonetse ibicuruzwa bitandukanye by'ibikoresho byo kumesa, kandi bikoreshwa mu gihe cyo kumesa.
Gukoresha isuku yo gukaraba intoki ni uburyo bwo guhitamo mu gihe tutagira isabune n'amazi ahagije.
Amazi yo gukaraba intoki arimo inzoga yagombye kuba afite nibura inzoga zingana na 60%.
Gukaraba intoki mu buryo bwa muganga byabaye ngombwa nyuma y'uko umuganga w'Umuhungari Ignaz Semmelweis avumbuye ko ari ingirakamaro (mu 1846) mu kwirinda indwara zandura mu bitaro.
Hariho ibikoresho bya elegitoroniki bifasha kwibutsa abakozi bo mu bitaro gukaraba intoki iyo bibukije kubikora.
Ubushakashatsi bumwe bwagaragaje ko ubwandu bugabanuka bitewe n'uko bikoreshwa.
Gukaraba intoki mu buryo bwa muganga bigomba kumara nibura amasegonda 15, ukoresheje isabune n'amazi cyangwa umunyu mu rugero rukwiriye, kugira ngo ukorore kandi usukure ibice by'amaboko.
Dukwiriye guhoberana.
Ukoresha umugozi kugira ngo ukureho umugozi uri munsi y'ukuboko, niba uriho.
Ni ngombwa ko ukaraba intoki neza kandi ukazisiga zikamye ukoresheje umwenda mwiza kuko hari udukoko dushobora gusigara mu mazi y'intoki.
Nyuma yo gukaraba intoki, fata igitambaro cyo gukingisha amazi (kandi ufungure inzugi zose z'amazi niba ari ngombwa).
Ibi ni ukubuza kongera kwandura indwara mu biganza no ku bice by'umubiri.
Intego yo gukaraba intoki mu bigo nderabuzima ni ukuvanaho virusi kandi ukirinda ko zandurira abandi.
Ikinyamakuru New British Medical Journal kivuga ko kudahanagura intoki bikomeje kuba ku kigero kitemewe mu bigo byinshi by'ubuvuzi, aho abaganga benshi n'abahanga mu buvuzi bibagirwa gukaraba intoki mbere yo kuvugana n'umurwayi, bigatuma habaho gukwirakwiza indwara z'ubuhumekero.
Ubushakashatsi bumwe bwagaragaje ko gukaraba intoki n'ibindi bikorwa byoroheje bishobora kugabanya ubwandu bw'amaraso bufitanye isano n'amaraso afata imyanda ku kigero cya 66%.
Amabwiriza y'ishami ry'umuryango wita ku isuku y'amaboko, ashobora kuboneka ku rubuga rwawo kugira ngo abantu bayagezeho.
Ubushakashatsi ku bintu bifitanye isano n'ibyo bwakorewe na Whitby et al.
Ibikoresho by'ubucuruzi birashobora gupima no gufungura intoki niba ibigaragara bisaba gushyiraho ingamba rusange.
Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima rivuga ko amasaha yo gukaraba intoki ari atanu:
Nyuma yo guhura n'amaraso cyangwa ibindi bikoresho byo mu mubiri
