Gucunga ibyago byo mu kazi bitewe n'aho ukorera n'aho ukorera, hashingiwe ku igenzura ry'ibyago bituruka ku guhura, ubukana bw'indwara mu baturage, n'ibyago by'umukozi ku giti cye bishobora guteza COVID-19.
