Abari mu kazi bafite ibyago byo kwiyongera, harimo abasaba guhura kenshi cyangwa cyane n'abantu batazi cyangwa bakekwaho COVID-19, ariko bashobora kwandura bitewe n'ubwandu bukomeje kuba mu baturage cyangwa ingendo mpuzamahanga.
