Iyi porogaramu imaze gukoreshwa mu mijyi 200 yo mu Bushinwa, naho muri Singapore ikoreshwa na porogaramu yitwa TraceTogether.
"Iyi porogaramu yashinzwe n'umuryango w'ikoranabuhanga wo mu karere, ikaba yasohotse ku mugaragaro kandi ikazatangwa na leta. Macedonia ya Ruguru yashyizeho porogaramu ya ""StopKorona!" ikoresha Bluetooth kugira ngo ikurikirane guhura n'abantu bashobora kwandura, kandi itange ibisubizo byihuse ku nzego z'ubuzima".
Iyi porogaramu yashyizweho n'ubushikiranganji bw'itumanaho n'ikoranabuhanga n'ubushikiranganji bw'ubuzima.
Ku ya 14 Mata 2020, porogaramu ya terefone yari itegereje kwemerwa na Google Play Store na Apple App Store.
"Ku ya 12 Mata, leta y'ubwami yemeje ko porogaramu yo kugenzura ibyiyumvo iri mu nzira yo gutangira kandi ko izatangira gukoreshwa mu byumweru biri imbere. Porogaramu nk'izo zateganyijwe muri Ireland no mu Bufaransa ("StopCovid"")".
Australia na Nouvelle Zelande birimo gusuzuma porogaramu yo gukurikirana TraceTogether na BlueTrace ya Singapore.Uburusiya bufite intego yo gushyiraho gahunda yo kwirinda virusi ya COVID-19 ku barwayi bafatwa na virusi itera SIDA baba mu mujyi wa Moscow, aho iyi porogaramu yashyizweho kugirango irinde kuva mu rugo.
Ross Anderson, umwarimu muri kaminuza ya Cambridge wigisha iby'umutekano mu by'ubwubatsi, yavuze ibibazo by'ukuri bishobora kuvuka mu gukoresha porogaramu zishingiye kuri sisitemu, harimo n'ibyiza bidashingiye ku kuri n'ibura ry'ibyiza iyo porogaramu ikoreshejwe ku mubare muto w'abaturage.
Mu rwego rwo gukemura impungenge z'ikwirakwira ry'imikorere ya virusi ya corona iteje urujijo cyangwa iteje akaga, Apple yashyizeho imipaka ku byiciro by'ibigo bishobora gushyiraho porogaramu zijyanye na virusi ya corona mu bubiko bwayo bwa App, ikabishyira ku byemezo byemewe cyangwa byemewe.
Google na Amazon byashyizeho ingamba nk'izo.
