Urukingo b'A COVID-19 ni urukingo rw'icyorezo cya Coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19).
Nubwo nta rukingo rwarangije kugeragezwa, hari izindi zikomeje kugeragezwa mu rwego rwo gukora urukingo nk'urwo.
Mu mpera za Gashyantare 2020, Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima ryavuze ko rititeze ko haboneka urukingo rwa SARS-CoV-2, virusi ihitana abantu, mu gihe kitarenze amezi 18.
Inkingo eshanu z'impanga zari mu cyiciro cya mbere cy'ubushakashatsi bw'umutekano mu kwezi kwa kane.
COVID-19 yamenyekanye mu Ukuboza 2019.
Icyorezo gikomeye cyibasiye isi yose mu 2020, cyatumye hashyirwaho amafaranga menshi mu bushakashatsi no gukora inkingo.
Ibigo byinshi birimo gukoresha iyi gene yatangajwe mu gukora urukingo rushobora kurwanya SARS-CoV-2.
Ibikorwa by'ingenzi by'umushinga wa CEPI wo gukora inkingo byavuzwe muri Mata ni umuvuduko, ubushobozi bwo gukora, gushyira mu bikorwa ku kigero no kugera ku isi yose.
Muri Mata, abahanga mu bya siyansi bo muri CEPI batangaje ko hari imbuga 10 zitandukanye za tekiniki zari ziri mu bushakashatsi no guteza imbere mu ntangiriro za 2020 mu rwego rwo gukora urukingo rukora neza ku cyorezo cya COVID-19.
Intego z'ibanze zageze ku cyiciro cya mbere cy'ubushakashatsi mu by'umutekano harimo:
Aside ya nikleyeri (DNA na RNA) (abashakashatsi mu cyiciro cya mbere n'urukingo rw'igerageza: Moderna, mRNA-1273)
Impamvu zitera virusi (bakora inkingo n'abakora igerageza ry'icyiciro cya mbere: CanSino Biologics, virusi ya adeno-vector type 5)
Nk'uko byagaragajwe n'itsinda ry'abahanga mu bya siyansi bo muri CEPI muri Mata, inkingo 115 z'igerageza ziri mu cyiciro cya mbere cy'iterambere, 78 muri zo zemeza ko ari zo zikiri mu mushinga (inkingo 79 nk'uko bivugwa n'Ikigo cya Milken), izindi 37 zashyizwe ahagaragara, ariko amakuru y'abaturage ni make (tuvuze ko ibintu biri mu igenamigambi no mu bikorwa byo guhanga).
Ibizamini by'icyiciro cya I-II bigenzura ibipimo by'umutekano n'ubwirinzi, by'umwihariko ibipimo by'imiti, kugenzura no mu bice bitandukanye, mu gihe hagaragazwa neza ibipimo by'ibyavuye mu bikorwa.
Ibizamini by'icyiciro cya kabiri bisaba abantu benshi, harimo n'abashinzwe kugenzura no gupima ubushobozi bw'urukingo mu kwirinda indwara, mu gihe hagenzurwa ingaruka nziza mu rugero rwiza.
"Mu bakandida 79 bakekwaho urukingo bari mu gikorwa cy'iterambere (byemejwe mu ntangiriro za Mata 2020), 74 ntibari mu igeragezwa ku bantu (bakomeje gukorwaho ubushakashatsi bwa ""pre-clinical""")."
