Ibizamini by'icyiciro cya III birimo gukorwa muri Amerika, Ubushinwa n'Ubutaliyani.Chloroquine, yakoreshwaga mu kuvura kanseri, yasuzumwe mu Bushinwa muri Gashyantare 2020 n'ibisubizo by'ibanze.
Ariko hari abantu basabye ko ubushakashatsi busubirwamo.
Ubuyobozi bw'ubuzima bw'igihugu cya Koreya n'ubw'u Bushinwa bwasabye ko hakoreshwa umuti wa Chloroquine.
Ariko kandi, Ikigo cya Wuhan Institute of Virology cyasabye ko umuntu yakoresha dosi imwe gusa, kandi ko iyo umuntu akoresheje 2 gusa, bishobora kumuhitana.
Ku ya 28 Werurwe 2020, ikigo cy'igihugu gishinzwe ikoreshwa ry'imiti FDA cyatanze itangazo ryemeza ko imiti ya hydroxychloroquine na chloroquine ikoreshwa mu buryo bwihutirwa mu kuvura abarwayi bafite COVID-19.
Ibipimo by'ibanze byerekana ko ingano yo hejuru ya ribavirin ari ngombwa mu guhagarika SARS-CoV-2 mu igerageza ry'ubuvuzi.
Nitazoxanide yasabwe ko yakomeza kwiga nyuma yo gusanga ifite ubushobozi buke bwo guhagarika SARS-CoV-2. Ibindi byasobanuye ko hari protein isohoka binyuze mu cyuma cya protease serine 2 (TMPRSS2), ari nayo nyirabayazana wa SARS-CoV-2 yinjira mu ngirabuzimafatizo binyuze mu cyuma cyakira ACE2.
Kwiga ku miti ya chloroquine na hydroxychloroquine, cyangwa kuyakoresha mu gihe ikoreshwa na azithromycin, ni ikibazo gikomeye, kuko hari inzego z'ubuvuzi zateye utwatsi ko iyi miti yagombye gukoreshwa nta bushakashatsi. Oseltamivir ntabwo ihagarika SARS-CoV-2 kandi nta ruhare ifite mu kuvura COVID-19.
Iyi cytocin ishobora kuba ari yo iteza ibibazo mu cyiciro cya nyuma cy'uburwayi bwa COVID-19.
Hari ibimenyetso byerekana ko hydroxychloroquine ishobora guhagarika ikwirakwira ry'imiterere y'uturemangingo twa cytokine.Tocilizumab yashyizwe mu buvuzi nyuma y'uko hakorwa ubushakashatsi buto, nk'uko byatangajwe na Komisiyo y'igihugu y'ubuzima mu Bushinwa.
Iri mu cyiciro cya kabiri cy'igerageza ritunguranye ku rwego rw'igihugu mu Butaliyani nyuma yo kugaragaza ibisubizo by'ingaruka mbi ku barwayi bakomeye.
Hamwe no gupima amaraso ya serum ya hydrochloride kugirango hamenyekane Cytokine Storms, bivuze kurwanya ihinduka nkiri ry'iyi virusi, ryibasira abantu bafite ingaruka zimwe na zimwe.
Umuti wo kuvura interloquin-6 wemejwe na FDA hashingiwe ku bushakashatsi bw'inyuma ku kuvura indwara yo kuvura sitokine ziterwa na sitoroide ziterwa n'imihangayiko iterwa n'imiterere itandukanye, mu mwaka wa 2017.
Kugeza ubu, nta bimenyetso bifatika bifatika byerekana ko tocilizumab ari umuti w'ingirakamaro wa CRS.
Kwimurira abantu bakira COVID-19 za antibodies zanduye kandi ziterwa n'ubwirinzi bw'umubiri ku bantu babikeneye, birimo kubonwa nk'uburyo bwo gukingira indwara zitari iz'urukingo.
Ubu buryo bwageragejwe kuri SARS ariko nta gisubizo gifatika cyabonetse.
Kugabanya ubwandu ni uburyo bwo gukora, aho umuti wa antibodies udakora ushobora gutuma ubwirinzi buhinduka ku buryo buhoraho ku cyorezo cya SARS-CoV-2.
Ariko hari izindi nzira zishoboka, urugero nka cytotoxin, ingirabuzimafatizo zishingiye kuri antibody na/cyangwa phagocytosis.
Urugero, ubundi buryo bwo kuvura intanga za androgen hakoreshejwe intanga za androgen z'imikorere ya monokondomu, buri mu nzira y'iterambere.
Ubundi, mu kuvura abantu bakira, amaraso y'abantu bakize aba afite intanga zikora ku bwoko runaka bwa virusi nshya.
Indwara za coronavirus ni ubwoko bw'indwara zifite ibimenyetso byinshi.
Li Wenliang, umuganga mu bitaro bikuru bya Wuhan, nyuma yaje kurwara COVID-19 arapfa nyuma yo gukwirakwiza ubumenyi ku ikwirakwira rya virusi.
